s.%20The%20Oberoi%20Group%20runs%20Trident%20Hotels%20and%20Oberoi%20Hotels%20%26amp%3B%20Resorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmitabh%20Kant%2C%20G20%20Sherpa%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20known%20him%20for%20two-and-a-half%20decades%E2%80%A6%20when%20I%20was%20working%20as%20tourism%20secretary%20in%20the%20Government%20of%20Kerala%E2%80%A6%20He%20was%20a%20perfectionist.%20By%20starting%20the%20Vilas%20chain%20%E2%80%93%20Amarvilas%20in%20Agra%20and%20Udaivilas%20in%20Udaipur%20%E2%80%93%20he%20created%20the%20best%20resort%20chain%20in%20India.%20He%20raised%20the%20profile%20of%20the%20Indian%20travel%20and%20hospitality%20sector.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EP.R.S.%20Oberoi%20took%20over%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20flagship%20of%20the%20Oberoi%20Group%20nearly%2021%20years%20ago%2C%20in%202002%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20his%20father%2C%20also%20the%20founding%20chairman%2C%20Mohan%20Singh%20Oberoi.%20He%20was%20CEO%20till%202013%2C%20when%20he%20stepped%20down%20and%20was%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Chairman%20Emeritus%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fp-r-s-oberoi-1929-2023-biki-oberoi-who-set-the-gold-standard-for-hospitality-9026737%2Flite%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20cites%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Puneet%20Chhatwal%2C%20MD%20and%20CEO%2C%20IHCL%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9C(He%20was)%20a%20true%20pioneer%20and%20icon%2C%20he%20leaves%20behind%20a%20legacy%20of%20impeccable%20hospitality%20that%20will%20be%20cherished%20forever%2C%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20transforming%20the%20industry%20landscape%20and%20elevating%20Indian%20hospitality%20on%20a%20global%20stage.%20The%20Oberoi%20Centre%20of%20Learning%20and%20Development%20founded%20by%20him%20has%20groomed%20generations%20of%20fine%20hoteliers%2C%20and%20he%20is%20deeply%20revered%20and%20respected%20by%20the%20many%20lives%20he%20touched.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorn%20on%20February%203%2C%201929%2C%20PRS%20Oberoi%20studied%20in%20India%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20and%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fbusiness%2Fstory%2Fprs-oberoi-dies-at-94-oberoi-group-chairman-emeritus-indian-hospitality-sector-doyen-2462548-2023-11-14%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20notes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20second-highest%20civilian%20honour%2C%20in%20January%202008.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Fbiz-tech%2F2023%2F11%2F14%2Fremembering-prithvi-raj-singh-oberoi-aka-biki-oberoi-group-patriarch-dies-at-94.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20writes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethat%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20also%20honoured%20with%20the%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Awards%20at%20ILTM%20(International%20Luxury%20Travel%20Market)%20and%20at%206th%20International%20Hotels%20Investment%20Forum%20in%20Berlin.%20He%20was%20also%20conferred%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Corporate%20Hotelier%20of%20the%20World%E2%80%99%20award%20by%20HOTELS%20magazine%20USA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20we%20honour%20the%20legacy%20of%20Mr.%20P.R.S.%20Oberoi%2C%20Chairman%20Emeritus%20of%20The%20Oberoi%20Group.%20His%20passion%20and%20attention%20to%20detail%20shaped%20our%20commitment%20to%20warm%2C%20sincere%2C%20and%20intuitive%20hospitality.%20This%20continued%20quest%20for%20excellence%20will%20drive%20us%20forward.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPRSOberoi%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23PRSOberoi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTheOberoiGroup%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TheOberoiGroup%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FII6yJxxCcs%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FII6yJxxCcs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Oberoi%20Hotels%20%26amp%3B%20Resorts%20(%40OberoiHotels)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOberoiHotels%2Fstatus%2F1724434510874616202%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EObituaries%20noted%20he%20was%20called%20%E2%80%98Biki%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Fprofile%2Fprs-biki-oberoi-indian-hotel-industry-chairman-emeritus-of-oberoi-group-bhuttos-friend-to-design-oberoi-intercontinental-42442%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20termed%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Ca%20stickler%20for%20time%20throughout%20his%20life%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20high%20point%20of%20Biki%20Oberoi%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20the%20hospitality%20industry%20was%20the%20moment%20he%20convinced%20his%20father%2C%20Sardar%20Mohan%20Singh%20Oberoi%20(M.S.%20Oberoi)%2C%20to%20assign%20architect%20and%20politician%20Piloo%20Mody%20to%20design%20Oberoi%20Intercontinental%20in%20the%20capital.%20That%20was%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20and%20many%20acclaimed%20architects%20of%20the%20country%20were%20keen%20to%20grab%20the%20lifetime%20opportunity%20to%20design%20the%20luxury%20hotel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20full%20page%20newspaper%20advertisements%20marking%20his%20demise%20and%20noting%20his%20career%20as%20a%20pioneer%20in%20luxury%20hospitality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2026%2C%202008%2C%20as%20armed%20attackers%20terrorised%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20Oberoi%20group%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20hotel%20in%C2%A0Mumbai%C2%A0was%20also%20under%20siege%20and%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Biki%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20per%20accounts%20of%20his%20life%2C%20note%20that%20he%20used%20to%20narrate%20the%20story%20of%20his%20childhood%20in%20Gujranwala%20(now%20in%20Pakistan).%20His%20father%2C%20MS%20Oberoi%2C%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20Ishran%20Devi%2C%20%E2%80%9Chad%20to%20flee%20their%20native%20village%2C%20Bhaun%2C%20in%20the%20early%201920s%20to%20safeguard%20their%20children%20from%20the%20outbreak%20of%20deadly%20plague.%20They%20moved%20to%20Muree%20(a%20hill%20station%20near%20Rawalpindi)%2C%20where%20M.S.%20Oberoi%20lived%20for%20some%20time%20doing%20odd%20jobs%20before%20moving%20to%20Shimla%20to%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPRS%20Oberoi%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20a%20devout%20and%20proud%20Sikh.%20He%20would%20often%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Fprofile%2Fprs-biki-oberoi-indian-hotel-industry-chairman-emeritus-of-oberoi-group-bhuttos-friend-to-design-oberoi-intercontinental-42442%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evisit%20Gurudwara%20Bangla%20Sahib%20for%20prayers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700032180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15123604%2FScreenshot-2023-11-15-at-12.35.0.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fprs-oberoi-biki-passes-away-tributes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Biki%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20per%20accounts%20of%20his%20life%20emerging%2C%20used%20to%20narrate%20the%20story%20of%20his%20childhood%20in%20Gujranwala%2C%20now%20in%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fprs-oberoi-biki-passes-away-tributes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20Cup%20Live%3A%20Team%20India%20Reaches%20Wankhede%20Ahead%20Of%20Kiwi%20Showdown%22%2C%22conte