trip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arms%20sought%20by%20Israel%20as%20it%20fights%20Hamas%2C%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20group%20by%20the%20US%20and%20European%20Union%2C%20are%20listed%20in%20a%20document%20labeled%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20Senior%20Leader%26quot%3B%20requests%20that's%20dated%20late%20October%20and%20is%20circulating%20in%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arms%20are%20already%20being%20shipped%20or%20the%20Defense%20Department%20is%20working%20to%20make%20them%20available%20from%20stockpiles%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%20according%20to%20the%20document%20reviewed%20by%20Bloomberg%20News.%20As%20of%20late%20October%2C%20for%20example%2C%20all%2036%2C000%20rounds%20of%2030mm%20cannon%20ammunition%2C%201%2C800%20of%20the%20requested%20M141%20bunker-buster%20munitions%20and%20at%20least%203%2C500%20night-vision%20devices%20were%20delivered%2C%20the%20tally%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Pentagon%20spokesman%20declined%20to%20discuss%20specifics%2C%20but%20the%20Defense%20Department%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bleveraging%20several%20avenues%20-%20from%20internal%20stocks%20to%20U.S.%20industry%20channels%20-%20to%20ensure%20Israel%20has%20the%20means%20to%20defend%20itself.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20security%20assistance%20continues%20to%20arrive%20on%20a%20near-daily%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20statement.%20It%20said%20the%20US%20was%20rapidly%20providing%20precision-guided%20munitions%2C%20small-diameter%20bombs%2C%20155mm%20artillery%20shells%20and%20other%20munitions.%20That's%20along%20with%20Iron%20Dome%20interceptors%20and%20medical%20support%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provision%20of%20artillery%20shells%20and%20other%20munitions%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20nongovernmental%20organizations%20that%20say%20the%20US%20supplies%20have%20allowed%20Israel%20to%20press%20ahead%20with%20a%20bombing%20campaign%20that%20Hamas-run%20health%20authorities%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20say%20have%20killed%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20Monday%2C%20more%20than%2030%20relief%20organizations%20wrote%20to%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20urging%20him%20not%20to%20send%20the%20155mm%20shells%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Gaza%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20densely%20populated%20places%2C%20155mm%20artillery%20shells%20are%20inherently%20indiscriminate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organizations%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20munitions%20are%20unguided%20and%20have%20a%20high%20error%20radius.%26quot%3B%20They%20said%20the%20shells%20often%20land%2025%20meters%20(82%20feet)%20away%20from%20the%20intended%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ammunition%20for%20AH-64%20Apache%20helicopter%20gunships%20includes%20about%202%2C000%20Hellfire%20Laser%20Guided%20missiles%20made%20by%20Lockheed%20Martin%20Corp.%2C%20some%20of%20which%20Israel%20has%20transferred%20to%20its%20forces%20as%20US%20Army%20teams%20seek%20supplies%20from%20stocks%20in%20Germany%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%20according%20to%20the%20tally.%20It%20also%20includes%20more%20than%2036%2C000%20rounds%20of%2030mm%20ammunition%20to%20be%20fired%20by%20the%20Apache's%20cannon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20defense%20forces%20have%20flown%20the%20Boeing-built%20Apaches%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20appears%20to%20be%20using%20the%20Apache%20helicopters%20%26quot%3Bto%20support%20Israel%20troops%20in%20contact%20with%20Hamas%20fighters%2C%20using%20their%2030mm%20chain%20guns%20against%20fighters%20caught%20out%20in%20the%20open%20and%20Hellfire%20missiles%20against%20vehicles%20and%20fighting%20position%20or%20bunkers%20used%20by%20Hamas%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Eisenstadt%2C%20director%20of%20military%20and%20security%20programs%20at%20the%20Washington%20Institute%20for%20Near%20East%20Policy%2C%20said%20in%20an%20email.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20may%20also%20be%20using%20Hellfires%20for%20the%20targeted%20killing%20of%20senior%20commanders%20when%20the%20opportunity%20presents%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReverse%20Trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20also%20requested%20more%20than%2057%2C000%20155mm%20High%20Explosive%20artillery%20shells%20and%2020%2C000%20M4A1%20rifles%2C%20as%20many%20as%205%2C000%20PVS-14%20night%20vision%20devices%2C%203%2C000%20M141%20hand-held%20bunker-buster%20munitions%20that%20US%20Central%20Command%20is%20supplying%2C%20400%20120mm%20mortars%20and%2075%20of%20the%20Army%20and%20Marine%20Corps'%20new%20Joint%20Light%20Tactical%20Vehicle%2C%20which%20is%20replacing%20the%20Hummer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20tally%2C%20the%20US%20has%20also%20donated%20its%20inventory%20of%20312%20Tamir%20missile%20interceptors.%20The%20Army's%20two%20Iron%20Dome%20batteries%20are%20traveling%20to%20Israel%20by%20sealift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weapons%20shipments%20include%20a%20reverse%20trip%20for%20155mm%20shells.%20The%2057%2C000%20had%20been%20sent%20from%20US%20stocks%20in%20Israel%20to%20US%20European%20Command%20locations%20to%20restock%20munitions%20that%20were%20sent%20to%20Ukraine%20for%20its%20fight%20against%20Russia's%20invasion.%20Now%20the%20restocked%20munitions%20are%20being%20sent%20back%20to%20Israel%20for%20its%20use%20in%20the%20conflict%20with%20Hamas%2C%20according%20to%20a%20congressional%20aide%20and%20US%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%20has%20provided%20more%20than%202%20million%20155mm%20shells%20and%20more%20than%20800%2C000%20105mm%20rounds%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20State%20Department%20summary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitchblade%20Drones%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20also%20requested%20200%20armor-piercing%20Switchblade%20600%20dive-bombing%20drones%20made%20by%20AeroVironment%20Inc.%20Ukraine%20has%20bought%20the%20drones%20directly%20from%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Army%20doesn't%20have%20any%20Switchblade%20600s%20in%20its%20inventory.%20It's%20unclear%20whether%20AeroVironment%20has%20the%20drones%20in%20stock%20or%20would%20need%20to%20build%20them.%20An%20AeroVironment%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20could%20steer%20Foreign%20Military%20Financing%20grants%20for%20purchase%20through%20the%20Foreign%20Military%20Sales%20process%2C%20according%20to%20an%20industry%20official%20familiar%20with%20the%20issue.%20DefenseScoop%2C%20a%20Washington-based%20defense%20technology%20newsletter%2C%20disclosed%20the%20Switchblade%20600%20request%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700031720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F9d388tog_gaza-bloomberg_625x300_15_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-is-quietly-sending-israel-ammunition-laser-guided-missiles-report-4575403%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pentagon%20has%20quietly%20ramped%20up%20military%20aid%20to%20Israel%2C%20delivering%20on%20requests%20that%20include%20more%20laser-guided%20missiles%20for%20its%20Apache%20gunship%20fleet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20155mm%20shells%2C%20night-vision%20devices%2C%20bunker-buster%20munitions%20and%20new%20army%20vehicles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-is-quietly-sending-israel-ammunition-laser-guided-missiles-report-4575403%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-is-quietly-sending-israel-ammunition-laser-guided-missiles-report-4575403%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3