html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-today-nov-15-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-gift-nifty-kalyan-jewellers-ask-automotive-123111500085_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20Al%20Shifa%20Hospital%2C%20The%20Latest%20Battleground%20In%20Israel-Hamas%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAl%20Shifa%20Hospital%2C%20raided%20by%20Israel%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20is%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States%20have%20said%20that%20Hamas%20militants%20were%20using%20Gaza's%20hospitals%20to%20hide%20command%20posts%20and%20hostages%20using%20underground%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20which%20has%20controlled%20the%20coastal%20enclave%20since%202007%2C%20has%20built%20a%20tunnel%20city%20stretching%20beneath%20Gaza%20for%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%2C%20up%20to%2080%20metres%20(87%20yards)%20deep%20in%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20health%20authorities%20and%20Shifa%20directors%20have%20denied%20that%20the%20group%20is%20concealing%20military%20infrastructure%20in%20or%20under%20the%20complex%20and%20have%20said%20they%20would%20welcome%20an%20international%20inspection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20Shifa%20Mean%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShifa%20is%20a%20sprawling%20complex%20of%20buildings%20and%20courtyards%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20from%20Gaza%20City's%20small%20fishing%20port%2C%20sandwiched%20between%20Beach%20refugee%20camp%20and%20the%20city's%20Rimal%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20name%20comes%20from%20the%20Arabic%20word%20%26quot%3Bhealing%26quot%3B%20-%20common%20for%20hospitals%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Many%20Babies%20Are%20In%20Al%20Shifa%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20was%20caring%20for%2036%20babies%20as%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20according%20to%20medical%20staff%20there%20who%20said%20there%20was%20no%20clear%20mechanism%20to%20move%20them%20despite%20an%20Israeli%20effort%20to%20supply%20incubators%20for%20an%20evacuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20original%2039%20premature%20babies%20have%20already%20died%20since%20Gaza's%20biggest%20hospital%20ran%20out%20of%20fuel%20at%20the%20weekend%20to%20power%20generators%20that%20had%20kept%20their%20incubators%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Was%20Al%20Shifa%20Built%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20built%20in%201946%20during%20British%20rule%2C%20two%20years%20before%20Britain%20withdrew%20from%20Palestine.%20It%20survived%20the%20Egyptian%20invasion%20in%201948%20and%20two%20decades%20of%20Egyptian%20military%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201967%2C%20Israel%20captured%20and%20occupied%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20Shifa%20remained%20a%20focal%20point%20-%20long%20before%20Hamas%20-%20where%20many%20Palestinians%20were%20taken%20during%20clashes%20with%20Israeli%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201971%2C%20the%20Times%20of%20London%20reported%20a%20gun%20battle%20took%20place%20between%20a%20Palestinian%20militant%20who%20hid%20under%20a%20bed%20in%20the%20nurses'%20quarters%20and%20an%20Israeli%20army%20patrol%20that%20was%20searching%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201987%2C%20during%20the%20opening%20week%20of%20the%20First%20Intifada%20against%20Israeli%20occupation%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20a%20confrontation%20when%20several%20hundred%20Palestinians%20outside%20Shifa%20threw%20rocks%20at%20Israeli%20soldiers%20while%20shouting%2C%20%26quot%3BCome%20and%20kill%20us%20all%20or%20get%20out!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Was%20The%20Hospital%20Redesigned%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20hospital%20complex%20was%20revamped%20and%20redesigned%20by%20Israeli%20architects%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZvi%20Elhyani%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Israel%20Architecture%20Archive%2C%20wrote%20on%20Ynet%20on%20Nov.%209%3A%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20aid%20of%20American%20support%2C%20Israel%20embarked%20on%20a%20project%20to%20revamp%20and%20enlarge%20the%20hospital%20complex.%20This%20undertaking%20also%20involved%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20subterranean%20concrete%20floor.%20In%20a%20grim%20twist%2C%20this%20underground%20area%20has%20been%20appropriated%20in%20recent%20years%20by%20Hamas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20without%20providing%20evidence%20of%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Did%20Hamas%20Take%20Control%20Of%20Al%20Shifa%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201994%2C%20Palestine%20Liberation%20Organization%20(PLO)%20leader%20Yasser%20Arafat's%20Fatah-dominated%20security%20forces%20saluted%20the%20Palestinian%20flag%20when%20it%20was%20raised%20over%20the%20hospital%20after%20Palestinians%20were%20granted%20limited%20self-autonomy%20in%20Gaza%20during%20the%20Oslo%20peace%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEffective%20control%20over%20it%20passed%20from%20the%20Fatah-dominated%20Palestinian%20Authority%20to%20Hamas%20after%20the%20Islamist%20group's%20surprise%202006%20election%20victory%20and%202007%20military%20takeover%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20power%20struggle%20between%20Fatah%20and%20Hamas%20building%20up%20to%20that%20takeover%2C%20fighters%20from%20both%20sides%20were%20treated%20at%20Shifa%20and%20other%20hospitals%2C%20under%20a%20form%20of%20truce%20that%20neither%20would%20harm%20the%20other%20side's%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20previously%20claimed%20that%20Hamas%20used%20underground%20areas%20in%20Shifa%20to%20hide%20-%20it%20said%20as%20much%20during%20a%202008-2009%20war%20in%20which%20more%20than%201%2C400%20Palestinians%20and%2013%20Israelis%20were%20killed.%20It%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20verify%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-gener