0the%20countries%2C%20India%2C%20China%20and%20all%20other%20countries%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2045-year-old%20leader%2C%20who%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20on%20Friday%2C%20said%20at%20his%20home%20in%20the%20capital%20Male.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20its%20pristine%20beaches%20and%20secluded%20resorts%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20holiday%20destinations%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20the%20Maldives%20has%20also%20become%20a%20geopolitical%20hotspot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20east-west%20shipping%20lanes%20pass%20the%20nation's%20chain%20of%201%2C192%20tiny%20coral%20islands%2C%20scattered%20around%20800%20kilometres%20(500%20miles)%20across%20the%20equator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20was%20regarded%20as%20a%20proxy%20of%20pro-China%20former%20president%20Abdulla%20Yameen%2C%20who%20had%20shifted%20the%20country%20heavily%20into%20Beijing's%20orbit%20till%20his%202018%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegional%20rivalry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20said%20he%20hoped%20to%20begin%20formal%20negotiations%20with%20New%20Delhi%20on%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20an%20estimated%2050%20to%2075%20Indian%20personnel%2C%20a%20sensitive%20campaign%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20the%20Maldives%20did%20not%20vote%20for%20me%20to%20allow%20any%20military%20presence%20in%20the%20Maldives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20British-educated%20civil%20engineer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20we%20are%20talking%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20remove%20them%2C%20and%20I'm%20sure%20we%20can%20do%20that%20in%20a%20peaceful%20and%20democratic%20manner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20said%20his%20mandate%20was%20to%20remove%20a%20unit%20of%20Indian%20security%20personnel%2C%20deployed%20to%20operate%20three%20aircraft%20gifted%20to%20the%20Maldives%20to%20patrol%20its%20vast%20maritime%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20asking%20for%20the%20Indian%20troops%20to%20leave%20our%20country%20to%20make%20room%20for%20any%20other%20country%20to%20bring%20their%20military%20troops%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20considered%20the%20Maldives%20with%20its%20population%20of%20about%20380%2C000%20Sunni%20Muslims%20to%20be%20within%20its%20sphere%20of%20influence%2C%20but%20had%20been%20worried%20about%20China's%20expanding%20footprint%20during%20Yameen's%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20has%20a%20history%20of%20entanglements%20with%20Male%2C%20including%20the%20deployment%20of%20soldiers%20to%20thwart%20a%201988%20coup%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaldives%20first%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20Maldives%2C%20it%20is%20very%20important%20that%20we%20put%20our%20interests%20first...%20also%20we%20want%20to%20work%20together%20with%20all%20the%20countries%2C%20have%20a%20good%20friendly%20relationship%2C%20cordial%2C%20candid%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20Muizzu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20nominated%20Muizzu%20after%20Yameen%20was%20barred%20from%20running%20for%20office%20following%20a%20criminal%20conviction%20of%20corruption%20during%20his%20five-year%20term%20when%20the%20country%20saw%20a%20spurt%20of%20Chinese-funded%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%2C%20a%20former%20housing%20minister%2C%20is%20credited%20with%20implementing%20Chinese-funded%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20including%20the%20construction%20of%207%2C000%20apartments%20and%20a%20landmark%20bridge%20linking%20the%20capital%20island%20Male%20with%20the%20nearby%20airport%20island%20of%20Hulhule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20situated%20in%20a%20very%20strategic%20location%2C%20in%20which%20many%20of%20the%20sea%20lanes%20of%20communication%20go%20across%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20inviting%20foreign%20investment%20to%20develop%20ports%20and%20logistics%20as%20well%20as%20set%20up%20a%20tax-free%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20said%20he%20was%20banking%20on%20completing%20the%20ambitious%20expansion%20of%20the%20international%20airport%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20jump-start%20an%20economy%20that%20was%20hit%20by%20heavy%20debt%20and%20a%20decline%20in%20tourism%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20hopeful%20of%20filling%20%26quot%3Bfunding%20gaps%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20nearly%20%241%20billion%20expansion%20of%20the%20Velana%20International%20Airport%2C%20which%20he%20sees%20as%20a%20gateway%20to%20attracting%20more%20foreign%20direct%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EClimate%20change%20threat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20country's%20public%20and%20government-guaranteed%20debt%20was%20about%20%247%20billion%2C%20or%20113.5%20percent%20of%20GDP%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20official%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20look%20at%20the%20economy%2C%20there's%20a%20huge%20debt%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed.%20The%20level%20of%20confidence%20of%20investors%20to%20come%20and%20invest%20in%20Maldives%20is%20really%20low%2C%26quot%3B%20Muizzu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20keen%20on%20expanding%20ports%20and%20harbour-related%20services%20to%20increase%20domestic%20earnings%2C%20while%20also%20looking%20for%20debt-free%20financing%20for%20his%20ambitious%20economic%20expansion%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20Muizzu%20said%20he%20was%20seeking%20up%20to%20%24500%20million%20in%20international%20funding%20to%20protect%20beaches%20and%20coral%20as%20warming%20and%20rising%20waters%20threaten%20his%20low-lying%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighty%20percent%20of%20the%20Maldives%20is%20less%20than%20a%20metre%20(three%20feet)%20above%20sea%20level%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20countries%20most%20threatened%20by%20rising%20sea%20levels%20linked%20to%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president-elect%20quoted%20a%20report%20that%20said%2060%20percent%20of%20corals%20had%20been%20bleached%20by%20rising%20water%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20coral%20has%20value%2C%20every%20waterway%20that%20is%20contaminated%20has%20a%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20insisting%20his%20country%20must%20be%20compensated%20for%20%26quot%3Bevery%20fish%20that%20dies%20due%20to%20global%20warming%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700028660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fgv2a8qa_mohamed-muizzu-reuters_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-troops-wont-replace-indian-soldiers-says-maldives-new-leader-4575287%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Maldives's%20incoming%20president%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20has%20called%20on%20Indian%20troops%20to%20leave%20after%20taking%20office%20later%20this%20week%2C%20but%20told%20AFP%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20redraw%20regional%20balance%20by%20bringing%20in%20Chinese%20forces%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-troops-wont-replace-indian-soldiers-says-maldives-new-leader-4575287%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-troops-wont-replace-indian-soldiers-says-maldives-new-leader-4575287%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-troops-wont-replace-indian-soldiers-says-maldives-new-leader-4575287%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Subrata%20Roy's%20Death%20Spotlights%20Rs%2025%2C000%20Crore%20Lying%20In%20SEBI%20Account%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20undistributed%20funds%20totalling%20over%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20lying%20with%20the%20capital%20markets%20regulator%20Sebi's%20account%20have%20come%20back%20into%20focus%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Sahara%20Group's%20chief%20Subrata%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Roy%20died%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20at%20the%20age%20of%2075%20after%20battling%20a%20prolonged%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20faced%20multiple%20regulatory%20and%20legal%20battles%20in%20connection%20with%20his%20group%20firms%20that%20were%20accused%20of%20circumventing%20regulations%20with%20Ponzi%20schemes%2C%20allegations%20his%20group%20always%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20capital%20markets%20regulator%20Sebi%20ordered%20two%20Sahara%20Group%20firms%20--%20Sahara%20India%20Real%20Estate%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(SIREL)%20and%20Sahara%20Housing%20Investment%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(SHICL)%20--%20to%20refund%20the%20money%20raised%20from%20nearly%203%20crore%20investors%20through%20certain%20bonds%20known%20as%20Optionally%20Fully%20Convertible%20Bonds%20(OFCDs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20order%20came%20after%20the%20regulator%20ruled%20that%20the%20funds%20were%20raised%20by%20the%20two%20firms%20in%20violation%20of%20its%20rules%20and%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%20process%20of%20appeals%20and%20cross-appeals%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20August%2031%2C%202012%20upheld%20Sebi's%20directions%20asking%20the%20two%20firms%20to%20refund%20the%20money%20collected%20from%20investors%20with%2015%20per%20cent%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahara%20was%20eventually%20asked%20to%20deposit%20an%20estimated%20Rs%2024%2C000%20crore%20with%20Sebi%20for%20further%20refund%20to%20investors%2C%20though%20the%20group%20has%20been%20maintaining%20that%20it%20had%20already%20refunded%20more%20than%2095%20per%20cent%20of%20investors%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20capital%20markets%20regulator's%20latest%20annual%20report%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(Sebi)%20issued%20Rs%20138.07%20crore%20in%20refunds%20over%2011%20years%20to%20investors%20of%20two%20Sahara%20Group%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20amount%20deposited%20in%20specially-opened%20bank%20accounts%20for%20the%20repayment%20has%20risen%20to%20more%20than%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20claims%20from%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20bondholders%20of%20the%20two%20Sahara%20companies%2C%20the%20total%20amount%20refunded%20by%20Sebi%20inched%20up%20by%20just%20about%20Rs%207%20lakh%20during%20the%20last%20fiscal%202022-23%2C%20while%20the%20balance%20in%20Sebi-Sahara%20refund%20accounts%20rose%20by%20Rs%201%2C087%20crore%20during%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20by%20the%20annual%20report%2C%20Sebi%20received%2019%2C650%20applications%20involving%2053%2C687%20accounts%20as%20of%20March%2031%2C%202023.%20Of%20these%2C%20%26quot%3Brefunds%20have%20been%20made%20concerning%2017%2C526%20applications%20involving%2048%2C326%20accounts%20for%20an%20aggregate%20amount%20of%20Rs%20138.07%20crore%2C%20including%20the%20interest%20amount%20of%20Rs%2067.98%20crore.%26quot%3B%20The%20remaining%20applications%20were%20closed%20due%20to%20their%20records%20not%20being%20traceable%20in%20the%20data%20provided%20by%20two%20Sahara%20Group%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20previous%20update%2C%20Sebi%20had%20put%20the%20total%20amount%20refunded%20by%20it%20as%20of%20March%2031%2C%202022%2C%20at%20Rs%20138%20crore%20concerning%2017%2C526%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Sebi%20said%20under%20various%20orders%20passed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20attachment%20orders%20passed%20by%20the%20regulator%2C%20an%20aggregate%20amount%20of%20Rs%2015%2C646.68%20crore%20has%20been%20recovered%20by%20it%20as%20of%20March%2031%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20amount%20along%20with%20the%20accrued%20interest%20after%20due%20refunds%20to%20the%20eligible%20bondholders%20was%20deposited%20in%20nationalised%20banks%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20judgment%20dated%20August%2031%2C%202012%2C%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20March%2031%2C%202023%2C%20the%20total%20amount%20deposited%20in%20nationalised%20banks%20is%20around%20Rs%2025%2C163%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20Sebi%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20amount%20stood%20at%20Rs%2024%2C076%20crore%2C%20Rs%2023%2C191%20crore%2C%20and%20Rs%2021%2C770.70%20crore%20as%20of%20March%2031%2C%202022%2C%20March%2031%2C%202021%2C%20and%20March%2031%2C%202020%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Centre%20in%20August%20started%20the%20process%20to%20refund%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20of%20depositors%20whose%20funds%20are%20struck%20in%20four%20cooperative%20societies%20of%20Sahara%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20Cooperation%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20launched%20the%20'CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal'%20in%20July%20to%20facilitate%20the%20return%20of%20the%20money%20to%20investors.%20Around%2018%20lakh%20depositors%20have%20been%20registered%20on%20the%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20that%20the%20money%20would%20be%20returned%20to%2010%20crore%20investors%20of%20the%20four%20cooperative%20societies%20within%209%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20followed%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20directing%20the%20transfer%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20from%20the%20Sahara-Sebi%20refund%20account%20to%20the%20Central%20Registrar%20of%20Cooperative%20Societies%20(CRCS).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700028660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-09%2Fsubrata-roy-650_650x400_41474620678.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsubrata-roy-death-subrata-roy-news-sahara-group-undistributed-funds-worth-over-rs-25-000