mu%20(nearest%20Myanmar%20town%20from%20Moreh)%20was%20over%20by%203%20pm%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20Army%20officer%20monitoring%20the%20exercise%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F39-myanmar-soldiers-who-entered-mizoram-sent-back%2Farticle67532430.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20also%20added%20that%20there%20were%20reports%20of%20two%20more%20Myanmarese%20soldiers%20crossing%20over%20into%20India%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours.%20He%20said%20they%20would%20also%20be%20sent%20back%20once%20security%20personnel%20locates%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20war%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20which%20has%20been%20on%20since%20February%202021%2C%20intensified%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20in%20the%20region%20close%20to%20the%20Mizoram%20border.%20The%20fighting%20between%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20Army%20and%20pro-democracy%20groups%2C%20including%20ethnicity-based%20extremist%20groups%2C%20has%20gone%20up%20by%20several%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Indian%20security%20officials%2C%20a%20fierce%20gunfight%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20two%20sides%C2%A0at%20Khawmawi%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20which%20is%20located%20across%20Zokhawthar%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Champhai%20district%20on%20Sunday%2C%20November%2012%20evening.%20About%201%2C500%20Myanmarese%20have%20been%20taking%20refuge%20in%20border%20areas%20of%20Mizoram%20following%20the%20gunfight%2C%20officials%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20ethnic%20armed%20groups%20aligned%20with%20the%20pro-democracy%20movement%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20Kuki%20Independent%20Army%2C%20Kuki%20National%20Army%2C%20and%20the%20Chinland%20Defence%20Force%20also%20attacked%20the%20Myanmarese%20military%20camp%20in%20Mizoram.%20A%20military%20camp%20in%20Rikhawdar%20near%20Khawmawi%20was%20also%20overrun%20by%20the%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFearing%20for%20their%20lives%2C%20the%2039%20soldiers%20ran%20for%20cover%20to%20reach%20Mizoram%20on%20Monday%20evening.%20The%20decision%20to%20allow%20Myanmarese%20soldiers%20into%20India%20resulted%20in%20protests%20from%20Chin%20refugees%20of%20Myanmar%2C%20who%20staged%20a%20protest%20outside%20the%20Zokhawthar%20police%20station%20where%20the%20soldiers%20were%20kept.%C2%A0The%20soldiers%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20according%20to%20a%20senior%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20outbreak%20of%20civil%20war%20in%20Myanmar%20in%20February%202021%2C%20Mizoram%20has%20been%20hosting%20more%20than%2035%2C000%20Chin%20refugees.%20They%20are%20taking%20refuge%20in%20schools%2C%20community%20halls%2C%20temporary%20sheds%2C%20and%20the%20homes%20of%20relatives%20across%20Mizoram.%20The%20refugees%20are%20taking%20shelter%20in%20schools%2C%20community%20halls%2C%20temporary%20sheds%2C%20and%20the%20homes%20of%20relatives%20across%20Mizoram.%20The%20Chins%20and%20Mizos%20of%20Mizoram%20belong%20to%20the%20Zo%20ethnic%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700027537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15111451%2FThe-Wire-77.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsecurity-forces-send-back-39-myanmar-soldiers-taking-refuge-in-mizoram%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20to%20send%20them%20back%20came%20after%20the%20camp%20in%20which%20the%20soldiers%20had%20been%20staying%20came%20under%20attack%20from%20ethnic%20armed%20groups%20aligned%20with%20the%20pro-democracy%20movement%20in%20Myanmar.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsecurity-forces-send-back-39-myanmar-soldiers-taking-refuge-in-mizoram%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farah%20Khan%20posts%20bday%20wish%20for%20BFF%20Sania%20Mirza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700027522000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105226211%2Cimgsize-135622.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffarah-khans-birthday-post-for-sania-mirza-is-bff-goals-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F105226200.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105226200.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESania%20Mirza%20is%20very%20close%20to%20many%20industry%20celebs.%20Parineeti%20Chopra%2C%20Farah%20Khan%2C%20Ananya%20Birla%20are%20like%20her%20best%20friends%20and%20she's%20often%20seen%20spending%20big%20occasions%20with%20them...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffarah-khans-birthday-post-for-sania-mirza-is-bff-goals-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F105226200.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fears%20Of%20Bedbug%20Invasion%20Sparks%20Panic%20Buying%20Of%20Insecticides%20In%20Hong%20Kong%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20have%20started%20panic-buying%20insect%20killers%20and%20hiring%20pest%20control%20services%20as%20fears%20over%20bedbugs%20in%20the%20city%20grow%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fhealth-environment%2Farticle%2F3241392%2Fhong-kong-bedbug-fears-spark-panic-buying-insecticides-and-leap-bookings-pest-control-firms%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%20Last%20week%2C%20a%20photo%20was%20widely%20circulated%20online%20in%20which%20bedbugs%20were%20seen%20on%20an%20Airport%20Express%20train.%20Later%2C%20after%20a%20deep%20cleaning%20process%2C%20no%20such%20insects%20were%20found%20on%20the%20train.%20However%2C%20the%20viral%20picture%20triggered%C2%A0paranoia%20among%20residents%20regarding%20a%20potential%20influx%20of%20bedbug%20infestation%20from%20South%20Korea%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Britain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20bedbugs%20are%20small%2C%20oval-shaped%20parasitic%2C%20nocturnal%20bloodsuckers%20and%20their%20bites%20can%20cause%20rashes.%C2%A0These%20blood-sucking%20pests%20have%20been%20given%20the%20name%20bedbugs%20because%20they%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20nesting%20in%20mattresses.%20They%20come%20out%20at%20night%20to%20feed%20on%20human%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Francisco%20Pazos%2C%20owner%20and%20head%20technician%20at%20pest%20control%20company%20Nobedbugs-HK%2C%20said%20the%20firm%20has%20an%20''unbelievable''%20amount%20of%20work%2C%20having%20''done%20a%20month's%20work%20in%20the%20last%20three%20days''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20''Hong%20Kong%20is%20like%20Disneyland%20for%20bedbugs...%20because%20it%20is%20so%20dense%2C%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20places%20for%20them%20to%20lay%20eggs%20but%20also%20move%20from%20person%20to%20person.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE-commerce%20platform%20Shopline%20has%20also%20seen%20a%20172%20times%20increase%20in%20sales%20of%20pest%20control%20and%20bedbug-killing%20products%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%C2%A0Hong%20Kong%20authorities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Fchina%2Fhong-kong-bedbugs-infestation-warning-b2444360.html%3Futm_term%3DAutofeed%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3DTwitter%23Echobox%3D1699528249%5C%22%3Edistributed%20bedbug%20warning%20leaflets%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20passengers%20at%20the%20airport%20amid%20rising%20reports%20of%20bedbug%20infestations%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20France%2C%20and%20the%20UK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hong%20Kong%20government%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20''Although%20information%20shows%20that%20bedbugs%20will%20not%20spread%20diseases%2C%20bedbug%20bites%20may%20cause%20skin%20allergy%20and%20itchiness%20and%20make%20people%20feel%20unwell.%20The%20government%20therefore%20takes%20swift%20actions%20to%20minimise%20the%20chance%20of%20transmission%20of%20bedbugs%20from%20overseas%20to%20the%20local%20community.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20expert%20said%20infestations%20of%20the%20insects%20could%20be%20avoided%20with%20good%20hygiene%20and%20simple%20precautions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20France's%20capital%20Paris%20also%20battled%20an%20invasion%20of%20bedbugs%2C%20just%2010%20months%20before%20the%202024%20Summer%20Olympics.%20The%20tiny%20pests%20were%20first%20spotted%20in%20hotels%20and%20rental%20apartments%20across%20the%20city%20during%20the%20summer.%20Moviegoers%20also%20reported%20spotting%20these%20bugs%20in%20theatres%20while%20some%20passengers%20caught%20them%20crawling%20around%20on%20seats%20in%20high-speed%20trains%20and%20Paris%20Metro.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBedbugs%20had%20disappeared%20from%20daily%20life%20in%20France%20in%20the%201950s%2C%20but%20their%20resurgence%20is%20mostly%20due%20to%20high%20population%20density%20and%20more%20mass%20transit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700026920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ff29rqqgo_bedbug_625x300_15_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffears-of-bedbug-invasion-sparks-panic-buying-of-insecticides-in-hong-kong-4575178%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Notably%2C%20bedbugs%20are%20small%2C%20oval-shaped%20parasitic%2C%20nocturnal%20bloodsuckers%20and%20their%20bites%20can%20cause%20rashes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffears-of-bedbug-invasion-sparks-panic-buying-of-insecticides-in-hong-kong-4575178%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffears-of-bedbug-invasion-sparks-panic-buying-of-insecticides-in-hong-kong-4575178%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2