darin%20after%20accepting%20the%20job%20offer%2C%20I've%20found%20it%20really%20easy%20to%20assimilate%2C%20as%20people%20are%20extremely%20friendly%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20figuring%20out%20a%20way%20to%20continue%20to%20stay%20here%20after%20my%20postdoctoral%20position%20ends%20has%20become%20my%20top%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20I%20don't%20need%20more%20than%20%2440%2C000%20a%20year%20to%20thrive%20in%20Taipei%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Dingxi%20neighbourhood%20in%20the%20Yonghe%20district%20of%20Taipei%2C%20where%20Alex%20Teachey%20lives.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6553102736d588dc55cfb9f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dingxi%20neighbourhood%20in%20the%20Yonghe%20district%20of%20Taipei%2C%20where%20Alex%20Teachey%20lives.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Teachey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20received%20the%20job%20offer%20to%20come%20to%20Taiwan%2C%20I%20thought%3A%20Wow%2C%20this%20salary%20is%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20low.%20But%20after%20living%20here%20for%20three%20years%2C%20I%20can%20safely%20say%20it's%20enough%20to%20live%20comfortably%20on%20in%20Taipei.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20in%20a%20three-bedroom%20apartment%20by%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20fourth-floor%20walk-up%20built%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20a%20typical%20Taiwanese%20family%20home.%20I%20pay%20around%20%24800%20in%20rent%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20in%20a%20neighborhood%20that%20I%20love%2C%20in%20New%20Taipei%20City%2C%20the%20enormous%20donut%20that%20sprawls%20around%20the%20center%20of%20Taipei.%20I%20live%20a%2020-minute%20bike%20ride%20from%20my%20office%20%E2%80%94%20I%20never%20could%20have%20have%20afforded%20anything%20remotely%20similar%20if%20I'd%20stayed%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20rent%2C%20the%20other%20big%20chunk%20of%20my%