e.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20president%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20White%20House%20before%20heading%20to%20San%20Francisco%20that%20the%20US%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20trying%20to%20decouple%20from%20China.%20What%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20change%20the%20relationship%20for%20the%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20he%20hoped%20to%20achieve%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20he%20said%20he%20wanted%20%26quot%3Bto%20get%20back%20on%20a%20normal%20course%20of%20corresponding%3B%20being%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20and%20talk%20to%20one%20another%20if%20there's%20a%20crisis%3B%20being%20able%20to%20make%20sure%20our%20(militaries)%20still%20have%20contact%20with%20one%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Biden%20also%20warned%20that%20the%20United%20States%20was%20wary%20of%20investing%20in%20China%20due%20to%20Beijing's%20business%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20sustain%20the%20support%20for%20positions%20where%20if%20we%20want%20to%20invest%20in%20China%2C%20we%20have%20to%20turn%20over%20all%20our%20trade%20secrets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20presidents%20are%20expected%20to%20meet%20for%20several%20hours%20Wednesday%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%20summit%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20forum%20brings%20together%2021%20economies%2C%20which%20together%20account%20for%20about%2060%20percent%20of%20the%20world%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20both%20also%20expected%20to%20meet%20major%20business%20leaders%20and%20hold%20a%20number%20of%20other%20bilateral%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpy%20balloon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPositive%20momentum%20from%20November%202022%20talks%20between%20Xi%20and%20Biden%20in%20Bali%20was%20derailed%20when%20the%20United%20States%20shot%20down%20what%20it%20said%20was%20a%20Chinese%20spy%20balloon%2C%20delaying%20a%20planned%20visit%20to%20Beijing%20by%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20a%20flurry%20of%20high-level%20diplomacy%2C%20including%20Blinken's%20eventual%20trip%20to%20China%20in%20June%2C%20has%20signaled%20a%20willingness%20on%20both%20sides%20to%20mend%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Beijing's%20expectations%20for%20the%20summit%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20China's%20foreign%20ministry%20was%20vague%2C%20mentioning%20%26quot%3Bin-depth%20communication%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20issues%20concerning%20world%20peace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20routinely%20warns%20it%20will%20not%20budge%20on%20issues%20it%20considers%20%26quot%3Bred%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20Taiwan%2C%20a%20self-ruling%20island%20off%20its%20coast%20that%20Beijing%20claims%20as%20its%20own%20territory%2C%20and%20its%20expansion%20into%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%20have%20recently%20made%20some%20progress%20on%20trade%20and%20economic%20relations%20as%20well%20as%20climate%20change%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20its%20Western%20allies%20once%20viewed%20emerging%20China%20as%20a%20friend%20in%20waiting%2C%20believing%20that%20as%20it%20became%20wealthier%2C%20it%20would%20become%20more%20liberal%20and%20fit%20in%20with%20the%20US-dominated%20global%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20that%20view%20has%20all%20but%20disappeared%20in%20Western%20capitals%20as%20the%20openness%20that%20heralded%20its%20hosting%20of%20the%202008%20Olympic%20Games%20has%20faded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20become%20more%20authoritarian%20under%20Xi%20and%20increasingly%20begun%20to%20throw%20its%20weight%20around%20on%20the%20international%20stage%2C%20including%20spending%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20on%20infrastructure%20development%20in%20third%20countries%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%26quot%3BBelt%20and%20Road%26quot%3B%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20making%20nice%20with%20China%20has%20fallen%20out%20of%20favour%20in%20Washington%2C%20as%20domestic%20politics%20have%20taken%20on%20an%20increasingly%20protectionist%20bent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20tendency%20accelerated%20under%20former%20president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20delighted%20his%20base%20by%20imposing%20punitive%20sanctions%20on%20Chinese%20imports%20in%20what%20he%20said%20was%20a%20bid%20to%20re-shore%20US%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20mood%20music%20has%20sweetened%20slightly%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20and%20Biden%20said%20Tuesday%20a%20less%20confrontational%20relationship%20with%20China%20would%20benefit%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20Chinese%20people%2C%20who%20are%20in%20trouble%20right%20now%20economically%2C%20if%20the%20average%20homeowner%2C%20if%20the%20average%20citizen%20in%20China%2C%20was%20able%20to%20have%20a%20decent%20paying%20job%20--%20that%20benefits%20them%2C%20and%20benefits%20all%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%20will%20have%20dinner%20with%20top%20US%20business%20leaders%20on%20his%20trip%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20push%20for%20a%20relaxation%20of%20US%20trade%20curbs%20in%20his%20talks%20with%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700023260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fnl0te4c4_biden-xi-650_625x300_14_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-xi-jinping-bidens-remark-on-chinas-real-problems-ahead-of-meeting-with-xi-4575027%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20Tuesday%20that%20China%20had%20%26quot%3Breal%20problems%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20prepared%20to%20meet%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20Xi%20Jinping%20for%20a%20summit%20in%20San%20Francisco%20aimed%20at%20repairing%20ties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-xi-jinping-bidens-remark-on-chinas-real-problems-ahead-of-meeting-with-xi-4575027%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-xi-jinping-bidens-remark-on-chinas-real-problems-ahead-of-meeting-with-xi-4575027%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-xi-jinping-bidens-remark-on-chinas-real-problems-ahead-of-meeting-with-xi-4575027%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20Subtle%20Art%20of%20Ignoring%20Concerns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15100751%2FUntitled-design-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemonetisation%E2%80%99s%20anniversary%20came%20and%20went%2C%20without%20any%20defence%20of%20the%20masterstroke%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Notebandi%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20man%20with%20a%20diploma%20in%20mechanical%20engineering%20from%20Latur%2C%20Maharashtra.%20Anil%20Bokil%20runs%20an%20institution%20called%20%E2%80%98ArthaKranti%E2%80%99%20(economic%20revolution)%2C%20and%20calls%20himself%20as%20an%20economic%20theorist.%20His%20thinking%3A%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%20where%2070%25%20of%20people%20survive%20on%20just%20Rs%20150%20per%20day%2C%20why%20do%20we%20need%20currency%20notes%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%20100%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20revealed%20in%20an%20interview%20days%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20abolished%2086%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20currency%20how%20the%20PM%20got%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202013%2C%20soon%20after%20Modi%20was%20declared%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20PM%20candidate%2C%20Bokil%20went%20to%20Ahmedabad%20with%20his%20colleagues%20and%20made%20a%20presentation%20about%20an%20ArthaKranti%20proposal.%20Modi%20gave%20Bokil%2010%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20the%20time%20I%20was%20done%2C%20I%20realised%20he%20had%20listened%20to%20me%20for%2090%20minutes.%20He%20said%20nothing%20after%20I%20made%20my%20presentation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20surprising.%20The%20idea%20that%20a%20simple%2C%20magical%20and%20transformational%20action%20could%20be%20executed%20would%20have%20transfixed%20Modi.%20On%20the%20ArthaKranti%20website%2C%20the%20benefits%20of%20demonetisation%20conveyed%20to%20Modi%20are%20listed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTerrorist%20and%20anti-national%20activities%20would%20be%20controlled%2C%20the%20motive%20for%20tax%20avoidance%20would%20be%20reduced%2C%20corruption%20would%20be%20minimised%2C%20(also)%20a%20significant%20growth%20in%20employment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20not%20to%20like%3F%20But%20there%20are%20no%20details%20about%20any%20of%20this%20nor%20how%20demonetisation%20would%20be%20executed%20and%20its%20benefits%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20reference%20to%20or%20analysis%20of%20what%20the%20fallout%20could%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArthaKranti%20also%20proposed%20withdrawing%20the%20entire%20taxation%20system%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20transaction%20tax%2C%20with%20a%20Rs%202%2C000%20limit%20on%20cash%20transactions.%20Its%20ideas%20were%20reductive%2C%20simplistic%20and%2C%20apparently%2C%20easy%20to%20implement.%20It%20was%20perfect%20for%20Modi%2C%20who%20picked%20out%20the%20single%20most%20dramatic%20element%20from%20this%3A%20demonetisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%20on%20November%208%2C%202016%2C%20Modi%20said%20India%E2%80%99s%20problems%20were%20corruption%2C%20black%20money%20and%20terrorism.%20Strong%20steps%20must%20be%20taken%20against%20these%2C%20and%20he%20would%20take%20them.%20Indians%20were%20honest%20but%20India%20was%20corrupt%2C%20and%20so%20a%20decisive%20step%20was%20needed%20against%20corruption%2C%20black%20money%20and%20terrorism.%20Had%20people%20ever%20thought%20about%20where%20money%20for%20terrorism%20came%20from%2C%20Modi%20asked.%20It%20came%20from%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20counterfeiting%20operations%20in%20India%2C%20which%20was%20proved%20by%20the%20frequent%20arrests.%20He%20said%20the%20circulation%20of%20cash%20was%20linked%20to%20corruption%3A%20this%20was%20why%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20notes%20were%20between%2080%25%20and%2090%25%20of%20the%20total%20currency.%20He%20was%20cancelling%20them%20as%20legal%20tender%20in%20four%20hours%2C%20at%20midnight.%20That%20meant%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20notes%20currently%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20anti-national%20people%20would%20become%20worthless%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-curious-case-of-the-missing-rbi-and-its-voice%5C%22%3EThe%20Curious%20Case%20of%20the%20Missing%20RBI%20and%20Its%20Voice%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20acknowledged%20there%20would%20be%20some%20discomfort%20through%20this%20policy%2C%20but%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20problem.%20Ordinary%20citizens%2C%20he%20said%2C%20were%20enthusiastic%20about%20sacrifice%20and%20hardship%20for%20the%20country.%20No%20preparation%20was%20made%20by%20various%20departments%20and%20we%20know%20this%20because%20the%20Cabinet%20was%20summoned%20on%20November%208%20and%20ministers%20were%20told%20to%20leave%20their%20mobiles%20behind%20so%20the%20act%20could%20remain%20secret%20till%20it%20was%20announced.%20Since%20ministers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%2C%20their%20departments%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20and%20nobody%20prepared%2C%20just%20as%20in%20the%20national%20lockdown%20of%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20had%20been%20specifically%20warned%20by%20the%20RBI%2C%20the%20body%20that%20actually%20had%20to%20demonetise%20the%20notes%20of%20currency%20its%20governor%20guaranteed%20with%20his%20signature%20and%20was%20arm-twisted%20into%20doing%20so%2C%20that%20demonetisation%20was%20a%20mistake.%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20resigned%20as%20governor%20after%20having%20discussed%20and%20disapproved%20of%20this%20move.%20The%20new%20governor%2C%20Urjit%20Patel%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20accept%20it%20by%20Modi%20within%20weeks%20of%20taking%20office.%20He%20then%20refused%20to%20release%20the%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting%20the%20RBI%20urgently%20held%20on%205.30%20pm%20on%20November%208%20(just%20before%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech)%20to%20approve%20the%20unhinged%20move%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FPolitics%2FuTs1pjrHeVUrpVJ6gPKNMP%2FRBI-cites-threat-to-life-national-security-as-Modis-noteb.html%5C%22%3Eciting%20national%20security%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%20to%20life%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20minutes%20were%20finally%20leaked%20to%20the%20press%20two%20years%20later%20in%20November%202018%2C%20Patel%20quit%20and%20left%20the%20following%20month.%20The%20RBI%20minutes%20said%20it%20was%20told%20by%20the%20government%20that%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20economy%20had%20grown%2030%25%20between%202011%20and%202016%20but%20the%20currency%20notes%20of%20higher%20denomination%20had%20grown%20at%20a%20much%20higher%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20cash%20was%20the%20facilitator%20for%20black%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20counterfeit%20money%20of%20around%20Rs%20400%20crores%20was%20in%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20notes%20should%20be%20made%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20government%20was%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20the%20economic%20growth%20referred%20to%20by%20the%20government%20was%20real%20while%20the%20rise%20in%20currency%20was%20nominal%20and%20not%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%20and%20%E2%80%9Chence%20this%20argument%20does%20not%20adequately%20support%20the%20recommendation%E2%80%9D%20for%20demonetisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20most%20black%20money%20was%20in%20land%20or%20gold%20and%20not%20cash%2C%20and%20abolishing%20currency%20would%20have%20no%20effect%20on%20curbing%20black%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20demonetisation%20would%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E*%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20Rs%20400%20crores%20in%20counterfeit%20currency%20was%20insignificant%20(only%200.02%25)%20compared%20to%20the%20total%20cash%20in%20circulation%3A%20Rs%2018%20lakh%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20all%20this%2C%20the%20RBI%20board%20nonetheless%20put%20its%20rubber%20stamp%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20idea.%20The%20reason%20why%20it%20fought%20to%20keep%20this%20capitulation%20secret%20is%20clear.%20It%20had%20done%20its%20job%20in%20pushing%20back%20and%20pointing%20out%20the%20flaws%3B%20it%20was%20now%20protecting%20Modi.%20That%20is%20why%20Urjit%20Patel%20shamefully%20claimed%20there%20was%20a%20national%20security%20reason%20as%20to%20why%20he%20could%20not%20reveal%20the%20minutes%2C%20when%20RTI%20activists%20sought%20to%20access%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20events%20proved%20that%20on%20every%20count%20the%20RBI%20had%20accurately%20predicted%20both%20the%20damage%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20benefit.%20What%20the%20RBI%20was%20hiding%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20Modi%20had%20ignored%20its%20concerns%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20true%20%E2%80%94%20and%20gone%20ahead%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700023130000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15100751%2FUntitled-design-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Faakar-patel-reserve-bank-of-india-demonetisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202016%2C%20the%20RBI%20had%20accurately%20predicted%20both%20the%20damage%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20benefit%20of%20the%20demonetisation.%20Was%20it%20heard%3F%20No.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Faakar-patel-reserve-bank-of-india-demonetisation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20says%20China%20has%20'real%20problems'%20ahead%20of%20key%20US%20summit%20with%20Xi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700023082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105224439%2Cimgsize-796422.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-says-china-has-real-problems-ahead-of-key-us-summit-with-xi%2Farticleshow%2F105224220.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105224220.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20expressed%20that%20China%20has%20%26quot%3Breal%20problems%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20fundraising%20event%20in%20San%20Francisco%20ahead%20of%20his%20meeting%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%20The%20leaders%20will%20meet%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20APEC%20summit%2C%20their%20first%20encounter%20in%20a%20year.%20Biden%20hopes%20to%20improve%20the%20strained%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20establish%20better%20communication.%20However%2C%20he%20also%20expressed%2