e.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22362%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22299%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavidas%20was%20a%20poet%20and%20philosopher%20who%20stood%20against%20initialised%20caste%20hierarchy%2C%20making%20him%20a%20significant%20spiritual%20symbol%20for%20Dalits%20today.%20However%2C%20in%20and%20around%20Makroniya%20town%2C%20where%20the%20memorial%20is%20being%20built%2C%20Dalit%20voters%2C%20though%20not%20opposed%20to%20a%20grand%20monument%20dedicated%20to%20Ravidas%2C%20said%20they%20had%20more%20pressing%20concerns%20such%20as%20basic%20civic%20amenities%20and%20employment%20opportunities.%20Many%20were%20suspicious%20of%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20project%2C%20a%20few%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20election%2C%20while%20others%20argued%20that%20building%20the%20job%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20backward%20Bundelkhand%20district%20would%20have%20been%20a%20better%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDev%20Kumar%20Ahirwar%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20electrician%2C%20viewed%20the%20Ravidas%20Temple%20as%20an%20election%20gimmick.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20employment%20created%20for%20us%20by%20the%20mandir%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%20They%20could%20have%20spent%20Rs%201-2%20crore%20on%20a%20temple%20and%20used%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20funds%20on%20generating%20employment%20by%20setting%20up%20a%20factory%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20would%20have%20really%20transformed%20Sagar%20district%20and%20provided%20people%20livelihood%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dalits%20in%20Ahirwar%E2%80%99s%20locality%2C%20a%20short%20distance%20away%20from%20where%20the%20project%20is%20being%20built%20in%20Badtuma%20village%2C%20complain%20about%20poor%20roads%2C%20lack%20of%20basic%20amenities%20and%20employment%20opportunities.%20For%20decades%20now%2C%20joblessness%20and%20drought%20conditions%20have%20forced%20lakhs%20of%20men%20and%20women%20to%20migrate%20from%20the%20region%20in%20search%20of%20better%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Ahirwar%2C%20an%20elderly%20Dalit%20labourer%2C%20said%20he%20was%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20would%20vote%20to%20change%20the%20government%20this%20election.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20building%20the%20temple%20will%20benefit.%20What%20will%20I%20get%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ram%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Ravidas%E2%80%99%20cultural%20significance%20for%20Dalits%20especially%20among%20the%20Raidasias%20and%20Jatavs%2C%20one%20might%20be%20cautious%20in%20dismissing%20the%20impact%20the%20memorial%20may%20have%20on%20the%20voters.%20For%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20symbolism%20is%20often%20an%20attractive%20political%20gesture.%20Even%20if%20we%20take%20that%20into%20consideration%2C%20livelihood%20issues%20seemed%20to%20dominate%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%20labourer%2C%20was%20miffed%20that%20his%20family%20was%20yet%20to%20get%20a%20pucca%20house%20from%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20power%20since%202003.%20His%20family%20has%20been%20living%20in%20the%20same%20house%2C%20today%20a%20semi-pucca%20thatched%20dwelling%2C%20for%20the%20past%20four%20decades.%20He%20says%20he%20sent%20several%20applications%20to%20the%20administration%20to%20get%20himself%20a%20land%20patta%20after%20he%20heard%20that%20the%20state%20was%20distributing%20them%20in%20his%20ward.%20But%20nothing%20happened%2C%20adding%20to%20his%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Ravidas%20Mandir%20is%20being%20built.%20The%20way%20I%20see%20it%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20house%20of%20god.%20But%20where%20will%20humans%20like%20us%20go%20when%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20house%20to%20stay%20in%3F%20Gods%20already%20occupy%20so%20much%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20feels%20the%20Congress%20government%20is%20more%20sympathetic%20towards%20the%20poor%20and%20marginalised%20communities%20while%20the%20BJP%20focuses%20on%20the%20dominant%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13160642%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-4.06.29-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22992%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13160642%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-4.06.29-PM.png%20992w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F13160642%2FScreenshot-2023-08-13-at-4.06.29-PM-300x156.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22516%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20Sagar.%20Photo%3A%20Video%20screengrab%2FTwitter%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2012%2C%20when%20Modi%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20the%20memorial%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-sagar-narendra-modi-ravidas-mughals%5C%22%3E%20he%20tried%20to%20pitch%20Ravidas%20against%20the%20Mughals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20plain%20terms%2C%20he%20was%20pitting%20a%20popular%20Dalit%20icon%20against%20Muslim%20rulers%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20fountainhead%2C%20the%20RSS%2C%20have%20for%20long%20demonised.%20Modi%20remembered%20Ravidas%20for%20his%20%E2%80%9Ccourage%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpatriotism%E2%80%9D%20in%20standing%20against%20subservience%20during%20the%20Mughal%20period%20when%20the%20Indian%20society%20grappled%20with%20%E2%80%98assaults%20on%20its%20faith%E2%80%99%20and%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%98erase%20its%20identity%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20were%20assaults%20on%20our%20faith%2C%20when%20restrictions%20were%20being%20imposed%20on%20us%20to%20erase%20our%20identity%2C%20even%20in%20those%20days%20%E2%80%93%20during%20the%20Mughal-period%20%E2%80%93%20look%20at%20the%20courage%20and%20patriotism%E2%80%A6Ravidas%20ji%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EParadheenta%20paap%20hai%2C%20jaan%20lehu%20re%20meet.%20Raidas%20paradheen%20sau%2C%20kaun%20kare%20hain%20preet%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%20translated%2C%20it%20means%3A%20dependency%20is%20a%20big%20sin%20and%20those%20who%20accept%20it%20and%20do%20not%20take%20a%20stand%20against%20it%20are%20not%20loved%20by%20anybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20200%20metres%20away%20from%20the%20construction%20site%2C%20exists%20a%20temple%20dedicated%20to%20Ravidas.%20The%20temple%20is%20quite%20popular%20among%20local%20Dalits%20who%20regularly%20visit%20its%20compound%20to%20attend%20bhandaras%20and%20wedding%20ceremonies.%20Bal%20Krishna%20Ahirwar%20has%20been%20the%20caretaker%20of%20the%20temple%20for%20the%20last%20three%20decades.%20He%20was%20unhappy%20that%20Modi%20didn%E2%80%99t%20visit%20the%20temple%20when%20he%20had%20come%20to%20lay%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20Ravidas%20project.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20put%20his%20feet%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bal%20Krishna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20BJP%20rule%2C%20Bal%20Krishna%20says%2C%20he%20did%20not%20get%20any%20major%20benefit%20from%20the%20government%20other%20than%20a%20pucca%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumbers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20population%20in%20Sagar%20district%20is%20Dalit.%20At%2021%25%20it%20is%20above%20the%20state%20average.%20Sagar%20is%20located%20in%20the%20backward%20and%20feudal%20Bundelkhand%20region%2C%20where%20the%20Dalit%20community%E2%80%99s%20vote%20is%20significant%20for%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20The%20other%20districts%20in%20Bundelkhand%20as%20well%20as%20the%20adjoining%20Gwalior-Chambal%20region%20also%20have%20a%20decent%20population%20of%20Dalits.%20In%20districts%20Chattarpur%2C%20Tikamgarh%2C%20Datia%2C%20Sagar%2C%20Panna%2C%20Morena%2C%20Bhind%2C%20Gwalior%2C%20Damoh%2C%20Ashoknagar%20and%20Shivpuri%20the%20SC%20vote%20ranges%20from%2018.7%25%20to%2025.46%20%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%202011%20Census.%20The%20Gwalior-Chambal%20and%20Bundelkhand%20regions%20have%20a%20total%20of%2060%20seats%20out%20of%20the%20230%20in%20MP.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20overwhelmed%20the%20BJP%20here%2C%20winning%2036%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20saffron%20party%20could%20only%20manage%2021.%20The%20BSP%20won%20two%20and%20the%20SP%20won%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082656%2FPSX_20231114_042359.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082656%2FPSX_20231114_042359.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082656%2FPSX_20231114_042359-300x210.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082656%2FPSX_20231114_042359-1024x717.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684785%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20design%20map%20of%20the%20under-construction%20Ravidas%20memorial%20complex%20in%20Sagar.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20collated%20by%20political%20analyst%20Ashish%20Ranjan%20shows%20that%20since%202008%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20performed%20well%20in%20the%2035%20seats%20reserved%20for%20the%20SC%20community%20in%20MP.%20The%20BJP%20has%20consistently%20maintained%20a%20vote%20share%20above%2040%25%20in%20these%20reserved%20constituencies.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20though%20lagging%20behind%20the%20BJP%20by%20a%20long%20stretch%2C%20has%20consistently%20grown%20in%20the%20SC%20reserved%20seats%20in%20the%20last%20three%20assembly%20elections.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20different%20thing%20that%20in%20the%20last%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%202014%20and%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20outperformed%20the%20Congress%20in%20reserved%20seats%20securing%2031%20and%2034%20out%20of%20the%2035%20assembly%20constituents%20with%20an%20overwhelming%20vote%20share%20of%2053.92%25%20and%2059.01%25.%20The%20Congress%20managed%20to%20lead%20in%20only%20four%20SC%20reserved%20constituencies%20in%202014%20and%20just%20one%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20held%20in%202008%2C%202013%20and%202018%2C%20the%20party%20recorded%20a%20consistent%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2025%20SC%20seats%20while%20the%20Congress%20won%20just%20nine.%20In%202013%2C%20the%20BJP%20bettered%20its%20position%2C%20winning%2028%20seats%20along%20with%20a%20huge%20jump%20in%20vote%20percentage%20from%2040.01%25%20in%202008%20to%2047.31%25%20in%202013.%20In%20the%20next%20election%20in%202018%2C%20however%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20seat%20tally%20reduced%20to%2018%20and%20its%20vote%20percentage%20dropped%20to%2042.14%25.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress%20which%20had%20won%20just%20four%20out%20of%2035%20SC%20reserved%20seats%20in%202013%2C%20performed%20reasonably%20well%20in%202018%20when%20it%20won%2017%20seats%20and%20its%20vote%20percentage%20jumped%20from%2036.45%25%20to%2042.44%25%2C%20even%20bettering%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20popular%20support%20by%20a%20thin%20margin.%20The%202018%20election%20was%20also%20one%20in%20which%20the%20Congress%20won%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%20While%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark%20by%20just%20two%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20formed%20the%20government%20with%20the%20support%20of%20four%20independents%2C%20two%20MLAs%20of%20the%20BSP%20and%20one%20of%20the%20SP.%20The%20government%20lasted%20only%2015%20months%20after%20the%20BJP%20toppled%20it%20through%20mass%20defections%20but%20observers%20say%20that%20the%20mandate%20in%202018%20reflected%20the%20strong%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMakroniya%20falls%20under%20the%20Naryawali%20reserved%20constituency.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20it%20by%20a%20thin%20margin%20of%208%2C900%20votes.%20In%20the%202013%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20seven%20out%20of%20the%20eight%20seats%20in%20Sagar%20district.%20In%202018%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Congress%20managed%20to%20win%20three%20out%20of%20eight%20seats%20in%20Sagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20neighbouring%20Khurai%20constituency%2C%20Dalits%20The%20Wire%20spoke%20to%20said%20overall%20livelihood%20issues%20were%20the%20most%20important%20factor%20while%20deciding%20whom%20to%20vote.%20Ramlal%20Ahirwar%2C%20who%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20makes%20bidis%20for%20a%20living%2C%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20had%20provided%20his%20family%20a%20tap%2C%20monetary%20assistance%20under%20the%20KISAN%20Samman%20Nidhi%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month%20under%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20scheme.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20proper%20road%20to%20his%20house.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20rains%2C%20our%20children%20are%20stranded%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20wife%2C%20as%20she%20rolled%20bidis%20in%20her%20courtyard%20while%20her%20husband%20cut%20the%20Tendu%20leaves%20into%20uniform%20squares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwasnt-my-mother-your-ladli-behna-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3EWasn%E2%80%99t%20My%20Mother%20Your%20Ladli%20Behna%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20earns%20Rs%20150%20for%20every%201%2C000%20bidis%20rolled.%20In%20Sagar%2C%20several%20politicians%20including%20elected%20representatives%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20bidi%20industry.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20in%20a%20study%20of%20the%20health%20hazards%20of%20the%20bidi%20industry%20in%20India%20said%20exposure%20to%20tobacco%2C%20nicotine%2C%20dust%20and%20other%20particles%20absorbed%20through%20skin%20and%20nasopharyngeal%20route%2C%20endangered%20the%20health%20of%20bidi%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamlal%2C%20though%20fairly%20content%20with%20his%20life%20conditions%2C%20feels%20a%20change%20in%20government%20might%20do%20his%20family%20good.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20new%20government%20will%20do%20new%20things%20and%20might%20provide%20us%20with%20new%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20same%20neighbourhood%2C%20the%20family%20of%20Meera%20Bai%2C%20also%20a%20bidi%20worker%2C%20feels%20continuity%20is%20better%2C%20as%20she%20praises%20the%20government%20for%20providing%20the%20poor%20free%20ration%20and%20Rs.%201%2C000%20monetary%20assistance%20to%20eligible%20adult%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20daughter%2C%20a%20first-time%20voter%2C%20also%20feels%20the%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20government%20will%20be%20better%20for%20her%20future.%20%E2%80%9COur%20Mamaji%20(maternal%20uncle%2C%20as%20Shivraj%20is%20called)%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20for%20our%20education%20so%20far%20and%20will%20definitely%20do%20a%20lot%20more%20in%20the%20future.%20We%20want%20him%20to%20continue%20ruling%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082620%2FPSX_20231114_042445-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082620%2FPSX_20231114_042445-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082620%2FPSX_20231114_042445-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082620%2FPSX_20231114_042445-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684782%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDalits%20who%20live%20in%20villages%20near%20the%20construction%20site.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELakhs%20and%20crores%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20also%20praised%20the%20government%20for%20providing%20laptops%20and%20scooters%20to%20meritorious%20girl%20students%20passing%20class%2012.%20In%20its%20election%20manifesto%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%20to%20turn%2015%20lakh%20rural%20women%20into%20%3Cem%3Elakhpatis%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20owners%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20%E2%80%93%20through%20skill%20training%20and%20provide%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20scheme%20with%20a%20pucca%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20voters%20also%20hoped%20that%20the%20petrochemical%20complex%20at%20Bina%20refinery%20of%20Bharat%20Petroleum%20Corporation%20Limited%20to%20be%20developed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20about%20Rs%2049%2C000%20crore%20in%20the%20same%20district%20would%20fetch%20employment%20opportunities.%20Modi%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20the%20project%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYatindra%20Singh%20Sisodia%2C%C2%A0director%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Science%20Research%2C%20Ujjain%2C%20said%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20extraordinary%20situation%20or%20factor%E2%80%9D%20visible%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%20when%20it%20came%20to%20Dalit%20votes%20this%20season.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20is%20a%20slight%20possibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20The%20Wire%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20they%20might%20improve%20from%20their%20previous%20performance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youth%20and%20educated%20class%20of%20Dalits%20are%20antagonized%20by%20atrocities%20and%20hierarchy%20in%20villages%20but%20the%20semi-literate%20and%20illiterate%20sections%20of%20beneficiaries%20may%20not%20be%20as%20triggered%2C%20said%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20may%20be%20trying%20to%20diffuse%20the%20negative%20sentiment%20against%20them%20among%20Dalits%20through%20moves%20like%20building%20a%20Ravidas%20Temple.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20don%E2%80%99t%20shift%20due%20to%20this%20gesture.%20It%20provides%20only%20a%20slight%20electoral%20benefit%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjan%20too%20argues%20that%20there%20was%20an%20anti-incumbency%20among%20Dalits.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20I%20cannot%20confirm%20the%20range%2C%20the%20Dalits%20appear%20to%20be%20tilting%20more%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20this%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDharmendra%20Ahirwar%2C%20a%20Dalit%20activist%2C%20who%20is%20contesting%20from%20an%20Aazad%20Samaj%20Party%20ticket%2C%20says%20his%20community%20does%20not%20view%20the%20Ravidas%20Memorial%20move%20as%20an%20earnest%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20care%20for%20Dalit%20sentiments.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20them%20to%20spend%20Rs%201%20crore%20on%20the%20temple%20and%20the%2099%20crores%20on%20industries%20that%20will%20benefit%20all%20groups.%20What%20good%20are%20a%20handful%20of%20shops%20that%20will%20open%20near%20the%20memorial%20complex%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDharmendra%2C%20though%20critical%20of%20both%20parties%2C%20feels%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20more%20harmful%20for%20Dalit%20interests%20than%20the%20Congress.%20The%20BJP%20is%20purely%20anti-Dalit%2C%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20recent%20cases%20of%20atrocities%20against%20the%20community%20in%20Sagar%20district%20alone.%20In%20August%2C%20a%20Dalit%20boy%20was%20lynched%20and%20his%20mother%20was%20publicly%20disrobed%20after%20the%20family%20refused%20to%20withdraw%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20complaint%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20sister%20had%20lodged%20against%20a%20man%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20a%20BJP%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20Dalit%20in%20Sagar%20district%20who%20is%20happy%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dharmendra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20individual%20cases%20of%20atrocities%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20lead%20to%20a%20pan-state%20or%20pan-region%20impact%20while%20voting%2C%20said%20Dalit%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082642%2FPSX_20231114_042311-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082642%2FPSX_20231114_042311-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082642%2FPSX_20231114_042311-1-300x208.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082642%2FPSX_20231114_042311-1-1024x710.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684784%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22832%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20site%20for%20the%20Ravidas%20temple.%20%E2%80%98This%20land%20is%20reserved%20for%20the%20temple%20of%20Sant%20Shiromani%20Ravidas%20ji%2C%E2%80%99%20reads%20the%20board.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lokniti-Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%C2%A0post-poll%20survey%20on%20MP%20election%20in%202018%20found%20that%20only%201.4%25%20of%20respondents%20picked%20caste%20discrimination%20as%20the%20single%20most%20important%20issue%20for%20voting.%20Less%20than%204%25%20picked%20reservation%2C%20while%20the%20majority%20ticked%20livelihood%20issues%3B%20jobs%20(18.7%25)%2C%20inflation%20(16%25)%20and%20development%20(8.8%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ravidas%20memorial%20will%20include%20an%20art%20museum%20and%20a%20gallery%20to%20showcase%20the%20life%20and%20philosophy%20of%20Ravidas%20along%20with%20a%20library%2C%20cafeteria%2C%20gazebo%2C%20bhakt%20niwas%20and%20a%20kund.%20The%20manager%20at%20the%20construction%20site%20said%20the%20project%20would%20be%20completed%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20prominent%20Ravidasia%20priest%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20the%20memorial%20would%20not%20have%20any%20great%20impact%20on%20the%20Dalit%20voters.%20The%20priest%20said%20the%20community%20members%20had%20demanded%20that%20an%20educational%20institute%2C%20hospital%20or%20a%20factory%20be%20built%20for%20the%20uplift%20of%20the%20society%20as%20well%20as%20to%20provide%20livelihood.%20Sagar%20district%20already%20has%20400-500%20big%20and%20small%20Ravidas%20temples%2C%20he%20said.%20Though%20Sagar%20has%20a%20central%20university%2C%20Dr.%20Hari%20Singh%20Gour%20University%2C%20the%20priest%20says%20local%20students%20from%20marginalized%20backgrounds%20are%20unable%20to%20compete%20with%20students%20who%20come%20from%20outside%20and%20are%20forced%20to%20pursue%20studies%20in%20Chhatarpur%2C%20a%20district%20where%20the%20famous%20Khajuraho%20Temple%20monuments%20are%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20line%20similar%20to%20the%20Ravidasi%20priest%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20Opposition%20Congress%20when%20its%20national%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20visited%20Sagar%20in%20August%20and%20promised%20to%20build%20a%20university%20dedicated%20to%20Sant%20Ravidas%20if%20they%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20Ravidasia%20sect%20and%20Dalits%20had%20earlier%20even%20demanded%20that%20the%20memorial%20be%20built%20at%20an%20alternative%20site%20in%20Karrapur%20village%20instead%20of%20the%20present%20location%20Badtuma%2C%20as%20the%20latter%20had%20no%20connection%20with%20the%20social%20reformer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Raidas%2C%20Jatav%2C%20Chamar%2C%20Mochi%2C%20Ahirwar%2C%20Regar%20and%20other%20related%20sub-castes%20make%20up%20for%20more%20than%2047%25%20of%20the%20Dalit%20population%20in%20MP.%20Since%20the%20BJP%2C%20Congress%2C%20BSP%20and%20Aazad%20Samaj%20Party%20have%20all%20fielded%20candidates%20from%20the%20same%20Ahirwar%20Dalit%20sub-sect%2C%20their%20votes%20were%20likely%20to%20be%20divided%2C%20said%20the%20priest%2C%20when%20asked%20if%20the%20community%20could%20mobilize%20behind%20one%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20the%20electoral%20battles%20play%20out%20in%20districts%20such%20as%20Sagar%20with%20significant%C2%A0Dalit%20population%20could%20eventually%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20determining%20who%20wins%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700018997000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15082631%2FPSX_20231114_042522-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-ravidas-temple-dalit-jobs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20electoral%20battles%20play%20out%20in%20districts%20such%20as%20Sagar%2C%20with%20significant%C2%A0Dalit%20populations%2C%20could%20eventually%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20determining%20who%20wins%20MP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-ravidas-temple-dalit-jobs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20military%20forces%20ra