n%20%E2%80%94%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20209%20Democrats%20joined%20Republicans%20in%20passing%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20Mike%20Johnson's%20%26quot%3Bladdered%26quot%3B%20short-term%20continuing%20resolution%20by%20a%20vote%20of%20336-95.%20The%20legislation%20would%20extend%20government%20funding%20for%20four%20spending%20bills%20until%20January%2019%2C%20while%20funding%20the%20remaining%20eight%20bills%20through%20February%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bill%20will%20stop%20the%20absurd%20holiday-season%20omnibus%20tradition%20of%20massive%2C%20loaded-up%20spending%20bills%20introduced%20right%20before%20the%20Christmas%20recess%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20usual%2C%20it%20was%20a%20rocky%20road%20to%20reach%20the%20passage%20of%20this%20legislation.%20The%20continuing%20resolution%20was%20clean%2C%20meaning%20it%20did%20not%20include%20the%20steep%20funding%20cuts%20many%20conservative%20lawmakers%20wanted%20as%20a%20condition%20to%20keep%20the%20government%20funded.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20just%20hours%20before%20the%20vote%2C%20the%20House%20Freedom%20Caucus%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffreedomcaucus%2Fstatus%2F1724419465050223062%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estatement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20opposing%20the%20legislation%20because%20it%20%26quot%3Bcontains%20no%20spending%20reductions%2C%20no%20border%20security%2C%20and%20not%20a%20single%20meaningful%20win%20for%20the%20American%20People.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRepublicans%20must%20stop%20negotiations%20against%20ourselves%20over%20fears%20of%20what%20the%20Senate%20may%20do%20with%20the%20promise%20'roll%20over%20today%20and%20we'll%20fight%20tomorrow%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20caucus%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20remain%20committed%20to%20working%20with%20Speaker%20Johnson%2C%20we%20need%20bold%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20now%20heads%20t