0focus%2C%20allowing%20Wall%20Street%20to%20predict%20who%20the%20top%20winners%20and%20losers%20could%20be.%20In%20fact%2C%20mentions%20of%20%26quot%3BEl%20Ni%C3%B1o%26quot%3B%20in%20earnings%20calls%20are%20already%20rising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExtreme%20weather%20events%20are%20broadening%20and%20strengthening%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20led%20by%20Javier%20Martinez%20de%20Olcoz%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20issued%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20micro%20effects%20are%20proliferating%2C%20and%20stocks%20are%20diverging.%20The%20macro%20effects%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20inflationary%2C%20if%20increased%20restrictions%20through%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20become%20more%20acute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20as%20a%20parched%20Panama%20Canal%20doesn't%20have%20enough%20water%20to%20let%20as%20many%20ships%20pass%20through%20the%20waterway%20as%20it%20once%20used%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUtilities%2C%20chemicals%2C%20global%20food%20retail%2C%20and%20chocolate%20are%20four%20stocks%20that%20have%20been%20already%20gutted%20this%20year.%20On%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20insurance%20stocks%20as%20well%20as%20Brazilian%20sugar%20and%20ethanol%20producers%20trading%20way%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20global%20utilities%20have%20more%20or%20less%20traded%20flat%2C%20while%20freight%20and%20shipping%20stocks%20have%20begun%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221292%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stocks%20potentially%20impacted%20by%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6553d17122cf74a5739720bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStocks%20potentially%20impacted%20by%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2C%20Mor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20stocks%2C%20commodities%20like%20olive%20oil%2C%20cocoa%2C%20and%20orange%20juice%20have%20felt%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20forecasts%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20an