ly%2C%20can%20get%20back%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20four%20months%20on%20strike%20%E2%80%93%20the%20longest%20legal%20action%20in%20its%20history%20%E2%80%93%20American%20actors%E2%80%99%20union%20SAG-AFTRA%20has%20agreed%20to%20a%20new%2C%20three-year%20deal%20with%20the%20Alliance%20of%20Motion%20Picture%20and%20Television%20Producers%20(AMPTP)%2C%20the%20group%20that%20represents%20the%20major%20studios%2C%20US%20television%20networks%20and%20streaming%20services%20like%20Netflix%2C%20Amazon%20and%20Apple%20TV%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%E2%80%99s%20members%20still%20need%20to%20formally%20approve%20the%20deal%20but%20most%20expect%20the%20vote%20will%20be%20strongly%20in%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actors%E2%80%99%20strike%2C%20and%20that%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhollywood-writers-reach-tentative-deal-with-studios%2Fa-66912366%5C%22%3EHollywood%E2%80%99s%20Writers%20Guild%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20WGA%2C%20which%20lasted%20from%20May%20through%20September%20this%20year%2C%20effectively%20shut%20down%20film%20and%20TV%20production%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20movies%20and%20series%20were%20able%20to%20secure%20interim%20agreements%20from%20the%20union%20to%20keep%20shooting%2C%20many%20hit%20shows%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3EEmily%20in%20Paris%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Last%20of%20Us%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ELaw%20and%20Order%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20White%20Lotus%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EYellowstone%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20blockbuster%20films%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EGladiator%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EAvatar%3C%2Fem%3E%20sequels%2C%20as%20well%20as%20new%20%3Cem%3ETransformers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESpider-Man%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESuperman%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0movies%2C%20were%20put%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20thousands%20of%20workers%2C%20both%20actors%20and%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cbelow-the-line%E2%80%9D%20employees%2C%20from%20set%20designers%20to%20audio%20technicians%20to%20make-up%20stylists%2C%20lost%20their%20jobs.%20The%20economic%20damage%20to%20the%20US%C2%A0economy%20runs%20into%20the%20billions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20also%20disrupted%20Hollywood%E2%80%99s%20promotional%20ecosystem%2C%20since%20actors%20were%20prohibited%20from%20promoting%20their%20movies%20at%20premieres%20and%20red%20carpet%20events%20while%20negotiations%20were%20still%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20films%2C%20notably%20%3Cem%3EDune%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EChallengers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20both%20starring%20Zendaya%2C%20delayed%20their%20releases%20until%20next%20year%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20stars%20will%20be%20available%20to%20promote%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOscar%20promotion%20can%20kick-off%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20of%20the%20strike%20is%20also%20a%20boon%20for%20the%20Oscar%20season%2C%20which%20can%20now%20kick%20off%20in%20earnest%20with%20award%C2%A0contenders%20available%20to%20do%20the%20rounds%20of%20talk%20shows%20and%20magazine%20profiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERestarting%20Hollywood%20could%20bring%20its%20own%20problems%2C%20however.%20As%20everyone%20rushes%20to%20get%20their%20movies%20and%20shows%20into%20production%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20risk%20of%20a%20bottleneck%20as%20demand%20for%20actors%2C%20cinematographers%2C%20editors%2C%20and%20costume%20designers%20outstrips%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20getting%20the%20dream%20machine%20going%20again.%20The%20studios%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20were%20desperate%20to%20reach%20a%20deal%20before%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%2C%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20salvaging%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20broadcast%20TV%20schedule%20and%20getting%20enough%20films%20shot%20and%20in%20the%20can%20before%20next%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%C2%A0issues%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20contract%20negotiation%2C%20the%20actors%20strike%20was%20about%20wages%2C%20and%20with%20the%20new%20deal%2C%20SAG-AFTRA%20secured%20a%20substantial%20bump%20in%20minimum%20rates%20%E2%80%93%20the%20base%20daily%20salary%20for%20a%20union%20actor%20on%20a%20film%20or%20TV%20shoot%20%E2%80%93%20for%20its%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20real%20battle%20was%20over%20the%20future.%20The%20new%20technologies%20of%20streaming%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20dominated%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHollywood%E2%80%99s%20creative%20classes%20felt%20global%20streamers%20weren%E2%80%99t%20properly%20compensating%20them%20for%20their%20work.%20An%20actor%20or%20writer%20on%20a%20television%20series%20typically%20gets%20paid%20an%20upfront%20salary%20plus%20compensation%2C%20or%20residuals%2C%20every%20time%20the%20show%20is%20rerun%2C%20or%20sold%20to%20a%20cable%20channel%20or%20international%20broadcaster.%20Netflix%20and%20co.%20broke%20that%20model%20by%20doing%20buy-out%20deals%2C%20paying%20talent%20a%20one-time%20lump%20sum%20to%20acquire%20a%20series%20worldwide%20to%20show%20on%20their%20platform%20in%20perpetuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20SAG-AFTRA%20deal%2C%20talent%20working%20on%20big-budget%20streaming%20series%20and%20movies%20will%20get%20a%20100%20percent%20bump%20in%20performance%20compensation%20bonuses%20if%20their%20work%20is%20a%20hit%2C%20meaning%20it%20crosses%20certain%20viewership%20thresholds.%20While%20this%20is%20unlikely%20to%20mean%20much%20for%20most%20union%20members%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bulk%20of%20Netflix%20series%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20hits%20%E2%80%94%20it%20marks%20a%20sea%20change%20by%20requiring%20streamers%20to%20share%20their%20profits%20with%20the%20people%20who%C2%A0make%20their%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Ft-42133476%5C%22%3EArtificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20an%20even%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fai-and-film-actors-and-writers-fear-obsolescence%2Fa-66307353%5C%22%3Ebigger%20sticking%20point%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20unions%20determined%20to%20limit%20how%20the%20studios%20and%20streamers%20could%20use%20new%20AI%C2%A0technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActors%20in%20particular%20were%20worried%20studios%20and%20streamers%20would%20begin%20to%20use%20AI%C2%A0scans%20of%20their%20likenesses%20and%20voice%20performances%20to%20insert%20them%20into%20new%20films%20and%20shows%20without%20their%20approval%20or%20compensation.%20This%20is%20a%20real%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBlack%20Widow%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0star%C2%A0Scarlett%20Johansson%20recently%20took%20legal%20action%20against%20an%20AI%C2%A0app%20that%C2%A0used%20her%20name%20and%20likeness%20in%20an%20online%20advertisement%20without%20her%20permission.%20Last%20month%2C%20Tom%20Hanks%20took%C2%A0to%20Instagram%20to%20warn%20his%20fans%20that%20a%20dental%20plan%20was%20using%20an%20unapproved%20AI-generated%20image%20of%20him%20for%20one%20of%20their%20promotional%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20SAG-AFTRA%20deal%20puts%20guardrails%20on%20the%20use%20of%20AI%C2%A0and%20requires%20producers%20to%20secure%20approval%20to%20scan%20and%20reuse%20an%20actors%E2%80%99%20performance.%20The%20AMPTP%20has%20also%20agreed%20to%20keep%20meeting%20with%20the%20union%20over%20the%20next%20two%20and%20half%20years%20until%20the%20next%20contract%20negotiations%2C%20to%20discuss%20AI%C2%A0as%20the%20technology%20advances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20shift%20in%20Hollywood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Hollywood%E2%80%99s%20fiercest%20labor%20dispute%20in%20a%20generation%20comes%20to%20a%20close%2C%20the%20creatives%2C%20not%20the%20suits%2C%20appear%20the%20clear%20winners.%20Most%20of%20SAG-AFTRA%E2%80%99s%20demands%20were%20met%20and%20the%20union%20secured%20concessions%20on%20the%20most%20contentious%20issues%2C%20including%20streaming%20compensation%20and%20restrictions%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solidarity%20within%20the%20union%20%E2%80%93%20big%20stars%20like%20George%20Clooney%2C%20Scarlett%20Johansson%2C%20and%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20expressed%20their%20support%20for%20the%20strike%2C%20alongside%20rank-and-file%20members%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20source%20of%20strength%20for%20SAG-AFTRA%20negotiators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20a%20power%20shift%20within%20Hollywood.%20The%20studios%20have%20reason%20to%20be%20worried.%20Their%20contract%20with%20the%20International%20Alliance%20of%20Theatrical%20Stage%20Employees%2C%20the%20union%20representing%20technicians%20and%20craftspersons%2C%20is%20due%20to%20end%20in%20November%202024.%20Another%20potential%20Tinseltown-shuttering%20strike%20looms%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhollywood-actors-strike-ends%2Fa-67343351%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699975839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14113622%2FSAG-AFTRA.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fwhat-lies-ahead-for-the-hollywood-as-actors-call-off-their-historic-strike%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20actors'%20union%20agrees%20to%20a%20new%20deal%20with%20studios%20and%20streaming%20services%20tentatively%20ending%20a%20four-month%20long%20strike.%20The%20deal%20shows%20a%20power%20shift%20in%20Hollywood.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fwhat-lies-ahead-for-the-hollywood-as-actors-call-off-their-historic-strike%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PRS%20Oberoi%3A%20Remembering%20the%20man%20who%20redefined%20the%20Indian%20hospitality%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699975766000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F14%2Ffull%2F1699951420-6924.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fprs-oberoi-remembering-the-man-who-redefined-the-indian-hospitality-123111401064_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20restaurateur%20inherited%20the%20business%20from%20his%20father%20Mohan%20Singh%20Oberoi%2C%20the%20pioneering%20founder%20of%20the%20group%20that%20now%20operates%2032%20hotels%20and%20has%20presence%20in%20seven%20countries%20under%20multiple%20brands%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fprs-oberoi-remembering-the-man-who-redefined-the-indian-hospitality-123111401064_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fprs-oberoi-remembering-the-man-who-redefined-the-indian-hospitality-123111401064_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fprs-oberoi-remembering-the-man-who-redefined-the-indian-hospitality-123111401064_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Levels%20of%20Fine%20Particulate%20Matter%20Peak%20Post-Diwali%2C%20Air%20Quality%20Drops%20in%20Several%20Cities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13184606%2FPollution.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Post-Diwali%2C%20several%20Indian%20cities%20have%20shown%20a%20peak%20in%20fine%20particulate%20matter%20(an%20air%20pollutant)%2C%20as%20per%20a%20preliminary%20analysis%20by%20the%20National%20Clean%20Air%20Programme%20(NCAP)%20Tracker%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20tracks%20India%E2%80%99s%20air%20quality%20data%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20NCAP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFine%20particulate%20matter%20or%20PM2.5%20are%20fine%2C%20inhalable%20particles%20%E2%80%93%20around%202.5%20mm%20in%20diameter%20%E2%80%93%20are%20produced%20due%20to%20the%20emission%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20such%20as%20coal.%20Fireworks%20are%20also%20known%20to%20temporarily%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F1660-4601%2F17%2F24%2F9333%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eincrease%20levels%20of%20PM2.5%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20atmosphere%20along%20with%20other%20pollutants%20such%20as%20sulfur%20dioxide%20in%20high%20concentrations.%20Such%20particulate%20matter%20can%20cause%20health%20concerns%20including%20respiratory%20ailments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHigher%20PM2.5%20post-Diwali%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFine%20particulate%20matter%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20considered%20a%20significant%20public%20health%20concern.%20Hence%2C%20PM2.5%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20pollutants%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20government-run%20air%20quality%20monitoring%20stations%20measure.%20According%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpcb.nic.in%2Fupload%2FNAAQS_2019.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECentral%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20under%20the%20National%20Ambient%20Air%20Quality%20Standard%20(NAAQS)%2C%20the%20safe%20level%20of%20annual%20PM2.5%20is%20set%20as%2040%20%CE%BCg%2Fm3%20and%20the%2024-hour%20average%20as%2060%20%CE%BCg%2Fm3.%20The%20National%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20also%20lists%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20limit%E2%80%9D%20for%20daily%20average%20PM2.5%3A%200-30%20%CE%BCg%2Fm3.%20The%20revised%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Firis.who.int%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F10665%2F345329%2F9789240034228-eng.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eglobal%20air%20quality%20guidelines%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20in%202021%2C%20however%2C%20set%20a%20stricter%20standard%3A%205%20%CE%BCg%2Fm3%20for%20an%20annual%20average%20and%2015%20%CE%BCg%2Fm3%20for%20a%2024-hour%20average.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NCAP%20Tracker%2C%20a%20policy%20tracker%20that%20keeps%20tabs%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20National%20Clean%20Air%20Programme%20and%20its%20effectiveness%2C%20and%20also%20analyses%20air%20quality%20data%20compiled%20from%20government-run%20monitoring%20stations%2C%20analysed%20the%20daily%20average%20PM2.5%20levels%20across%2011%20cities%20in%20the%20country%20over%20three%20days%20%E2%80%93%20a%20day%20before%20Diwali%20(November%2011)%2C%20the%20day%20of%20Diwali%20(November%2012)%20and%20a%20day%20after%20Diwali%20(November%2013).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2011%20cities%20are%20Bengaluru%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Patna.%20The%20festival%20of%20Diwali%20is%20marked%20by%20aerial%20fireworks%20in%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Studies%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS2590162119300553%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethis%20one%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202020%20have%20shown%20that%20fireworks%20during%20the%20festival%20days%20%E2%80%9Ccontribute%20to%20an%20increase%20of%20PM2.5%20loading%20in%20Delhi%20significantly%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NCAP%20Tracker%E2%80%99s%20preliminary%20analyses%20for%20this%20year%2C%20PM%202.5%20levels%20on%20this%20Diwali%20and%20for%20the%2012%20hours%20after%20(till%20noon%20on%20November%2013)%20were%20above%20the%20CPCB%E2%80%99s%20daily%20average%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%20limit%20of%2030%20ug%2Fm3%20in%20all%20the%20cities%20analysed.%20Patna%20in%20Bihar%20showed%20the%20highest%20average%20PM%202.5%20level%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Diwali%202023%20(November%2012)%2C%20at%20206.1%20ug%2Fm3.%20This%20is%20around%2013.7%20times%20more%20than%20the%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20daily%20safe%20limit%20of%2015%20ug%2Fm3.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDelhi%20leads%20in%20spike%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2013%20(from%20midnight%20to%2012%20pm)%2C%20Delhi%20recorded%20the%20highest%20PM2.5%20average%20of%20300.9%20ug%2Fm3.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20Delhi%20also%20witnessed%20the%20highest%20spike%20(recorded%20at%2015-minute%20intervals)%20%E2%80%93%20at%20999.5%20ug%2Fm3%20at%20Pusa%20on%20November%2013%20at%201%3A30%20am).%20Several%20other%20capital%20cities%20also%20experienced%20extremely%20high%20PM2.5%20levels%20on%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20Diwali%20and%20the%20following%20day%20(November%2013)%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20compare%20levels%20of%20PM2.5%20%E2%80%93%20or%20any%20other%20pollutant%20across%20years%20%E2%80%93%20unless%20other%20confounding%20factors%20are%20at%20play%20such%20as%20wind%20speed%20and%20rainfall%20(which%20will%20affect%20PM2.5%20levels%20and%20make%20it%20vary%20from%20year%20to%20year%20in%20each%20city)%20are%20accounted%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAarti%20Khosla%2C%20director%20of%20Climate%20Trends%2C%20which%20runs%20NCAP%20Tracker%20along%20with%20Respirer%20Living%20Sciences%2C%20suggests%20a%20drastic%20step%3A%20phasing%20out%20the%20firecracker%20industry%20itself%20over%20the%20next%202-3%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CStemming%20supply%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20in%20a%20press%20release%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20the%20only%20way%20to%20asphyxiate%20demand%20in%20this%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20Supreme%20Court%20ban%20in%20Delhi%20NCR%20was%20flouted%20fully%20and%20shows%20that%20a%20different%20approach%20where%20the%20centre%20and%20state%20must%20work%20together%20is%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhasing%20out%20firecrackers%20may%20seem%20an%20extreme%20step%20for%20many%20while%20%E2%80%9Cenvironment-friendly%E2%80%9D%20fireworks%20are%20now%20available.%20These%2C%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubs.acs.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1021%2Facs.est.0c03521%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresearchers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20emit%2015-65%25%20less%20particulate%20matter.%20However%2C%20the%20researchers%20also%20found%20that%20such%20fireworks%20still%20deteriorate%20air%20quality%20rather%20significantly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThree%20Indian%20cities%20among%20the%20most%20polluted%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20Swiss%20technology%20company%20IQAir%2C%20which%20measures%20live%20air%20quality%20(PM2.5%20levels)%20using%20data%20from%20monitoring%20stations%20and%20sensors%20operated%20by%20a%20range%20of%20organizations%20including%20governmental%20bodies%20and%20research%20institutions%2C%20three%20Indian%20cities%20are%20among%20the%20top%20ten%20cities%20across%20the%20world%20that%20have%20the%20most%20polluted%20air.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%203%20pm%20on%20November%2014%2C%20Delhi%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iqair.com%2Fworld-air-quality-ranking%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eleading%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20the%20most%20polluted%20city%20(highest%20PM2.5%20levels%20across%20the%20world)%2C%20with%20an%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20of%20306.%20The%20AQI%20here%20is%20measured%20based%20on%20WHO%20standards%20and%20the%20ideal%20limit%20is%20an%20annual%20PM2.5%20level%20of%205%20%CE%BCg%2Fm3.%20The%20IQAir%20lists%20an%20AQI%20of%20more%20than%20300%20as%20%E2%80%9CHazardous%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20this%20extreme%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20health%20warning%20of%20emergency%20conditions.%20The%20entire%20population%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20severely%20affected%2C%E2%80%9D%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iqair.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fhazardous-air-quality%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIQAir%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMumbai%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20was%20in%20fourth%20place%2C%20with%20an%20AQI%20of%20156%20%E2%80%93%20which%20falls%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunhealthy%E2%80%9D%20category.%20Kolkata%20came%20ninth%2C%20with%20an%20AQI%20of%20127%2C%20which%20is%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunhealthy%20for%20sensitive%20groups%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699973112000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13184606%2FPollution.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fas-levels-of-fine-particulate-matter-peak-post-diwali-air-quality-drops-in-several-cities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Patna%20showed%20the%20highest%20average%20PM%202.5%20level%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Diwali%202023%20(November%2012)%2C%20at%20206.1%20ug%2Fm3.%20This%20is%20around%2013.7%20times%20more%20than%20the%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20daily%20safe%20limit%20of%2015%20ug%2Fm3.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fas-levels-of-fine-particulate-matter-peak-post-diwali-air-quality-drops-in-several-cities%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Perfect%20Winter%20Getaway%3A%208%20Himalayan%20Homestays%20You%20Can%20Snuggle%20In%20to%20Enjoy%20Snowfall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20states%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20temperatures%20soar%20to%20an%20unbearable%2045%20degrees%2C%20snow%20was%20an%20enigma%20for%20me.%20I%20would%20often%20watch%20it%20captured%20on%20television%20and%20wonder%20how%20it%20would%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20father%2C%20who%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20young%20adult%20life%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20