nchanting%20outdoors%20become%20even%20more%20swoon-worthy%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20starts%20to%20snow%2C%20most%20likely%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20offering%20magnificent%20views%2C%20this%20place%20provides%20guests%20with%20the%20opportunity%20to%20take%20a%20stroll%20through%20the%20nearby%20forest.%20With%20amenities%20like%20WiFi%2C%20a%20bonfire%2C%20and%20the%20best%20part%20%E2%80%93%20the%20flexibility%20to%20bring%20along%20your%20furry%20friends%2C%20this%20homestay%20is%20a%20haven.%20Hosted%20by%20Daleep%2C%20who%20guides%20you%20through%20walks%20in%20the%20surrounding%20apple%20and%20pear%20orchards%2C%20as%20well%20as%20wheat%20and%20maize%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrice%3A%20Rs%205%2C999%20per%20night%20for%20the%20cottage%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBook%20your%20stay%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airbnb.co.in%2Frooms%2F23780166%3Fsource_impression_id%3Dp3_1603785195_aVYGoe%252FCs8fdW9x%252F%26guests%3D4%26adults%3D4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252FStreetWayHolidays%252Fphotos%252Fa.848745308550473%252F4449662595125375%252F%253Ftype%253D3%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22792%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Pinewood%20Sunrise%2C%20Kasauli%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20cosy%20homestay%20that%20offers%20you%20a%20sense%20of%20peace%20and%20quiet%20is%20Pinewood%20Sunrise.%20There%20is%20no%20wifi%20or%20television%20here%20but%20you%20know%20what%20will%20keep%20you%20busy%20%E2%80%94%20the%20enchanting%20view%20of%20Dhauladhar%20range%20of%20the%20Himalayas%20and%20the%20perfume%20of%20pine%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20has%20cosy%20rooms%20with%20