0Uttarakhand%3F%20Check%20out%20the%2010%20best%20homestays%20that%20you%20can%20book%20to%20enjoy%20snowfall.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334115%2Fbest-homestays-in-himachal-pradesh-uttarakhand-to-enjoy-snowfall-in-winter%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Painting%20on%20Mud%20Walls%20to%20Winning%20Padma%20Shri%3A%20How%20Durgabai%20Took%20Gond%20Iconography%20To%20The%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20Gond%20artist%20Durgabai%20Vyam%E2%80%99s%20Bhopal%20home%20would%20easily%20pass%20off%20as%20a%20studio.%20Bedecked%20in%20canvas%20paintings%2C%20with%20drawings%20on%20the%20mud%20walls%20interspersing%20this%20art%2C%20the%20home%20is%20a%20riot%20of%20colour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dindori-born%20artist%20was%20deprived%20of%20a%20school%20education%20%E2%80%94%20a%20result%20of%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20meagre%20income%20%E2%80%94%20but%20absorbed%20things%20happening%20around%20her%20faster%20than%20other%20children%20her%20age.%20As%20her%20%3Cem%3Edadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(grandmother)%20would%20put%20the%20last%20finishing%20touches%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333532%2Fpadma-shri-t-s-satyan-father-of-indian-photojournalism-mysuru-bengaluru-history-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintricate%20paintings%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20home%E2%80%99s%20mud%20walls%2C%20a%20young%20Durgabai%20watched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArt%2C%20therefore%2C%20was%20her%20first%20subject%2C%20a%20love%20she%20carried%20with%20her%20through%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20Dindori%2C%20I%20would%20paint%20on%20the%20walls%20using%20white%20mud%20(%3Cem%3Echuhi%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20red%20mud%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20black%20mud%20(charcoal%20black).%20Festivals%20and%20weddings%20in%20the%20vil