s%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmha-extends-ban-on-10-meitei-extremist-organisations-under-uapa-for-another-five-year%2Farticle67528452.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20notification%20said%20the%20outfits%20have%20been%20engaging%20in%20activities%20prejudicial%20to%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%20by%20employing%20and%20engaging%20in%20armed%20means%20to%20achieve%20their%20objectives.%20Towards%20this%20end%2C%20they%20have%20been%20attacking%20and%20killing%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20police%20and%20civilians%20in%20Manipur.%20They%20are%20also%20indulging%20in%20acts%20of%20intimidation%2C%20extortion%2C%20and%20looting%20of%20the%20civilian%20population%20for%20collection%20of%20funds%2C%20the%20notification%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisations%20have%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20making%20contacts%20with%20sources%20abroad%20to%20influence%20public%20opinion%20and%20for%20securing%20their%20assistance%20by%20way%20of%20arms%20and%20training%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20achieving%20their%20secessionist%20objective%20and%20maintaining%20camps%20in%20neighbouring%20countries%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20sanctuaries%2C%20training%2C%20and%20clandestine%20procurement%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extended%20ban%2C%20which%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20November%2013%2C%20will%20remain%20in%20force%20for%2010%20years%20hence.%20According%20to%20the%20previous%202018%20notification%2C%20the%20said%20outfits%20were%20involved%20in%20756%20violent%20incidents%20from%20January%201%2C%202013-%20July%2031%2C%202018%2C%20and%20killed%2086%20persons%2C%20including%2035%20security%20personnel%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20notification%2C%20however%2C%20omitted%20reference%20to%20the%20number%20of%20violent%20incidents%20the%20organisations%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699971348000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F10074930%2FNorth_Block_Ministry_of_home_affairs-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentre-extends-ban-against-eight-meitei-extremist-organisations-for-10-years%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Calling%20them%20'unlawful%20association'%20under%20the%20UAPA%20law%2C%20the%20MHA%20notification%20said%20the%20outfits%20have%20been%20inciting%20people%20of%20Manipur%20for%20secession.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentre-extends-ban-against-eight-meitei-extremist-organisations-for-10-years%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Braving%20Threats%20by%20Land%20Mafia%2C%20Techie%20Turns%2025-Acre%20Barren%20Land%20Into%20a%20Forest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Gudiyatham%20in%20Vellore%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20G%20Srikanth%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature.%20He%20would%20walk%20to%20school%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332580%2Fmillet-based-startups-helping-farmers-ragi-jowar-international-year-of-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassing%20a%20forest%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20the%20way%2C%20and%20would%20enjoy%20listening%20to%20the%20chirping%20birds%20and%20insects.%20After%20an%20idyllic%20childhood%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20and%20worked%20as%20an%20assistant%20director%20in%20the%20movies.%20He%20recalls%20coming%20home%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98concrete%20jungle%E2%80%99%20to%20take%20a%20whiff%20of%20fresh%20air.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20every%20visit%20to%20Gudiyatham%20felt%20different.%20Srikanth%20saw%20the%20green%20cover%20reduce%20slowly%3B%20all%20but%20vanishing%20in%20front%20of%20his%20eyes.%20He%20felt%20disheartened%20that%20his%20hometown%20was%20also%20