-work-view-16-1699969285-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334096%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20land%20before%20and%20after%20Srikanth%20planted%207%2C000%20trees.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202018%2C%20Srikanth%20started%20planting%201%2C000%20trees%20on%20the%20roadside%20of%20Ulli%20village%20in%20Gudiyatham.%20He%20also%20took%20responsibility%20for%20maintaining%20the%20trees%2C%20and%20in%20six%20short%20months%2C%20they%20grew%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20used%20to%20be%20a%20social%20forest%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Palar%20river%2C%20that%20I%20would%20cross%20on%20my%20way%20to%20school%20every%20day.%20It%20was%20slowly%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20land%20mafia%20and%20all%20the%20trees%20were%20cut.%20It%20became%20a%20barren%20wasteland%20which%20was%20just%20used%20for%20sand.%20I%20wanted%20to%20restore%20and%20recreate%20that%20forest%2C%20which%20was%20home%20to%20so%20many%20birds%2C%20insects%20and%20monkeys.%20I%20would%20keep%20giving%20petitions%20to%20the%20district%20collector%20every%20week%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srikanth%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20social%20forestry%20is%20to%20involve%20locals%20of%20the%20region%20in%20the%20afforestation%20of%20unused%20wastelands%2C%20and%20to%20also%20protect%20and%20preserve%20them%20from%20rapid%20deforestation.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20social%20forest%2C%20people%20can%20come%20and%20go%20unlike%20a%20reserved%20forest%2C%20where%20no%20one%20is%20allowed%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Srikanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20saw%20many%20monkeys%20getting%20hurt%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20which%20bothered%20him%20greatly.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20birds%20and%20monkeys%20would%20be%20wounded.%20They%20had%20no%20place%20to%20go%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%201%2C000%20trees%20that%20he%20planted%20grew%20well%2C%20his%20efforts%20were%20noticed%20by%20the%20local%20authorities%20and%20reached%20the%20attention%20of%20then%20collector%2C%20A%20Shanmuga%20Sundaram.%20Srikanth%20recalls%20that%20Sundaram%20offered%20him%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20Sundaram%20to%20help%20him%20build%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332547%2Fsooraj-purushothaman-organic-farmer-kerala-gardening-growing-vegetables%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20social%20forest%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Palar%20riverbed%2C%20and%20restore%20it%20to%20its%20yesteryear%20glory.%20The%20collector%20gave%20him%202%20acres%20of%20that%20land.%20Srikanth%20worked%20hard%20and%20planted%20500%20trees%20in%20that%20area%2C%20all%20at%20his%20own%20expense.%20However%2C%20the%20land%20mafia%20was%20not%20happy.%20They%20threatened%20Srikanth%20verbally%20and%20physically%2C%20and%20slapped%20a%20case%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.16.13-1699969363.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srikanth%20has%20built%20the%20forest%20on%20the%20Palar%20riverbed%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.16.13-1699969363.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.16.13-1699969363-300x244.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.16.13-1699969363-500x406.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-med