ing%5C%22%3EHe%20planted%20native%20trees%20and%20fruits%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20like%20jamun%2C%20peepal%2C%20fig%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201040px)%20100vw%2C%201040px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srikanth%20invested%20Rs%201.5%20lakhs%20to%20build%20the%20forest%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426.jpeg%201040w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334105%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESrikanth%20invested%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20to%20build%20the%20forest.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20social%20forest%2C%20built%20on%20the%20riverbed%2C%20can%20help%20prevent%20soil%20erosion%2C%20according%20to%20environmental%20scientist%20Praveen%20Kumar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20is%2C%20say%20100%20acres%20of%20land%20under%20paddy%20cultivation%2C%20people%20would%20build%20a%20small%20forest%20in%20between%2C%20to%20help%20cross%20pollination.%20The%20birds%20and%20snakes%20in%20the%20forest%20would%20keep%20rats%20and%20insects%20away%20from%20the%20crops