eland-volcano-why-everything-points-towards-an-eruption-but-scientists-dont-know-exactly-where-or-when-13008200%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Curator%20Ranjit%20Hoskote%20Resigns%20from%20German%20Arts%20Panel%20Due%20to%20Row%20Over%202019%20Statement%20Critical%20of%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F16120251%2FhmvmTUr5_400x400.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mumbai-based%20author%20and%20curator%2C%20Ranjit%20Hoskote%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-flux.com%2Fnotes%2F575318%2Fdocumenta-resignation-letter%5C%22%3Ehas%20resigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Finding%20Committee%20for%20the%20upcoming%2016th%20edition%20of%20Documenta%20in%20Kassel%2C%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDocumenta%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F09%2F23%2Farts%2Fdesign%2Fdocumenta-15.html%5C%22%3Eworld%E2%80%99s%20most%20prestigious%3C%2Fa%3E%20art%20exhibition%2C%20which%20takes%20place%20every%20five%20years%20in%20Kassel%2C%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20resignation%20follows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sueddeutsche.de%2Fkultur%2Franjit-hoskote-documenta-antisemitismus-bds-1.6301063%3Freduced%3Dtrue%5C%22%3Ean%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20daily%20%3Cem%3ES%C3%BCddeutsche%20Zeitung%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20November%209%2C%202023.%20It%20accused%20Hoskote%20of%20BDS%20%5BBoycott%2C%20Divestment%20and%20Sanctions%20against%20Israel%5D%20sympathies%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-Semitism%2C%E2%80%9D%20based%20on%20his%20signing%20of%20a%202019%20BDS%20petition%20against%20a%20far-right%20event%20on%20%E2%80%9CZionism%20and%20Hindutva%2C%E2%80%9D%20co-hosted%20by%20the%20Consulate%20General%20of%20Israel%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGermany%E2%80%99s%20Green%20Party%20culture%20minister%2C%20Claudia%20Roth%2C%20condemned%20the%20statement%20as%20%E2%80%9Cclearly%20anti-Semitic%E2%80%9D%20for%20depicting%20Zionism%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cracist%20ideology%E2%80%9D%20and%20Israel%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csettler-colonial%20apartheid%20state.%E2%80%9D%20Roth%20warned%20of%20withdrawing%20state%20funding%20for%20Documenta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20edition%20as%20well%2C%20the%20exhibition%20was%20engulfed%20in%20a%20scandal%20around%20its%20alleged%20proximity%20to%20BDS%20and%20a%20dispute%20over%20anti-Semitic%20iconography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20future%20developments%20for%20German%20cultural%20institutions%2C%20Documenta%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20members%20of%20the%20new%20Finding%20Committee%2C%20and%20particularly%20the%20next%20artistic%20director(s)%2C%20held%20no%20BDS%20sympathies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20another%20member%20of%20the%20new%20Finding%20Committee%20resigned%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Israeli%20painter%20Bracha%20Ettinger%2C%20for%20reasons%20that%20she%20stated%20were%20not%20connected%20to%20the%20accusations%20levelled%20against%20Hoskote%20but%20because%20Israel%20was%20enduring%20%E2%80%9Cdark%20times.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoskote%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20escalating%20scandals%20that%20have%20followed%20an%20anti-BDS%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20German%20parliament%20in%202019%2C%20with%20artists%20and%20curators%2C%20especially%20from%20non-European%20backgrounds%2C%20increasingly%20finding%20themselves%20targeted%20by%20weaponised%20accusations%20of%20anti-Semitism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20text%20of%20Hoskote%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%2C%20November%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDear%20Professor%20Dr.%20Andreas%20Hoffmann%20(managing%20director%2C%20Documenta%20und%20Museum%20Fridericianum%20gGmbH)%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20last%20few%20days%20have%20been%20among%20the%20most%20deeply%20distressing%20days%20of%20my%20life.%20The%20monstrous%20charge%20of%20anti-Semitism%20has%20been%20brought%20against%20my%20name%20in%20Germany%2C%20a%20country%20I%20have%20regarded%20with%20love%20and%20admiration%2C%20and%20to%20whose%20cultural%20institutions%20and%20intellectual%20life%20I%20have%20contributed%20for%20several%20decades%2C%20as%20a%20writer%2C%20curator%2C%20and%20cultural%20theorist.%20Members%20of%20the%20German%20commentariat%20who%20have%20no%20acquaintance%20with%20my%20life%20and%20work%20have%20judged%2C%20denounced%2C%20and%20stigmatized%20me%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20single%20signature%20on%20a%20petition%2C%20taken%20out%20of%20its%20context%20and%20not%20approached%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20reason.%20I%20have%20been%20written%20about%20with%20harshness%20and%20condescension%2C%20and%20none%20of%20my%20detractors%20has%20thought%20it%20important%20to%20ask%20me%20for%20my%20point%20of%20view.%20I%20feel%2C%20strongly%2C%20that%20I%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20the%20proceedings%20of%20a%20kangaroo%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20to%20me%20that%20there%20is%20no%20room%2C%20in%20this%20toxic%20atmosphere%2C%20for%20a%20nuanced%20discussion%20of%20the%20issues%20at%20stake.%20And%20now%E2%80%94in%20what%20strikes%20me%20as%20a%20doomed%20attempt%20to%20save%20a%20situation%20that%20is%20beyond%20saving%E2%80%94I%20am%20being%20asked%20to%20accept%20a%20sweeping%20and%20untenable%20definition%20of%20anti-Semitism%20that%20conflates%20the%20Jewish%20people%20with%20the%20Israeli%20state%3B%20and%20that%2C%20correspondingly%2C%20misrepresents%20any%20expression%20of%20sympathy%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20as%20support%20for%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20conscience%20does%20not%20permit%20me%20to%20accept%20this%20sweeping%20definition%20and%20these%20strictures%20on%20human%20empathy.%20Such%20a%20definition%20and%20such%20strictures%20have%20been%20opposed%20by%20prominent%20Jewish%20thinkers%20such%20as%20the%20philosopher%20Omri%20Boehm%2C%20the%20historian%20Moshe%20Zimmermann%2C%20the%20columnist%20Gideon%20Levy%2C%20the%20philosopher%20Michael%20Marder%2C%20and%20many%2C%20many%20others%2C%20who%20reject%20the%20equation%20of%20anti-Zionism%20with%20anti-Semitism.%20A%20system%20that%20insists%20on%20such%20a%20definition%20and%20such%20strictures%E2%80%94and%20which%20chooses%20to%20ignore%20both%20criticality%20and%20compassion%E2%80%94is%20a%20system%20that%20has%20lost%20its%20moral%20compass.%20I%20say%20this%20with%20the%20greatest%20sadness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20pains%20me%20to%20say%20that%20such%20circumstances%20negate%20Documenta%E2%80%99s%20historic%20openness%20to%20a%20diversity%20of%20positions%20and%20its%20capacity%20for%20sustaining%20the%20life%20of%20the%20imagination%20in%20a%20supportive%20environment.%20I%20greatly%20fear%20that%20these%20circumstances%20will%20compromise%20the%20generosity%20of%20spirit%20and%20the%20willingness%20to%20engage%20in%20dialogue%20that%20have%20long%20been%20sterling%20features%20of%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20global%20cultural%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20unable%20to%20perform%20my%20duties%20towards%20Documenta%2C%20an%20institution%20for%20which%20I%20have%20had%20great%20affection%20and%20which%20I%20have%20known%20well%20for%20more%20than%20twenty%20years%2C%20ever%20since%20Okwui%20Enwezor%20invited%20me%20to%20chair%20a%20panel%20at%20the%20Delhi%20platform%20of%20Documenta%2011%20in%20May%202001.%20It%20has%20been%20an%20honor%20to%20serve%20on%20the%20Finding%20Committee%20for%20Documenta%2016%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20a%20pleasure%20to%20get%20to%20know%20you%20and%20work%20with%20you.%20With%20much%20regret%2C%20I%20must%20offer%20you%20my%20resignation%20and%20step%20down%20from%20the%20Finding%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E***%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20leave%2C%20you%20will%20agree%20that%20it%20is%20only%20fair%20that%20I%20should%20be%20permitted%20to%20state%20my%20side%20of%20this%20case%2C%20for%20the%20record.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20do%20this%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20I%20wish%20to%20restate%20that%20I%20have%20the%20highest%20regard%20for%20the%20Jewish%20people%2C%20and%20have%20always%20had%20the%20deepest%20empathy%20with%20their%20historic%20sufferings%20and%20admiration%20for%20their%20glorious%20cultural%20achievements.%20This%20is%20evident%20in%20my%20essays%2C%20my%20lectures%2C%20and%20my%20books.%20I%20am%20appalled%20by%20the%20accusation%20that%20I%20am%20anti-Semitic%2C%20and%20the%20suggestion%20that%20I%20am%20in%20need%20of%20instruction%20on%20this%20sensitive%20subject.%20Simple%20biographical%20factors%20render%20this%20accusation%20absurd.%20I%20was%20brought%20up%20in%20a%20pluralist%20family%2C%20which%20took%20pride%20in%20the%20diversity%20of%20India%2C%20including%20the%20presence%2C%20among%20us%2C%20of%20three%20distinct%20Jewish%20communities%E2%80%94the%20Bene%20Israel%2C%20the%20Cochin%20Jews%2C%20and%20the%20Baghdadi%20Jews%E2%80%94for%20centuries.%20My%20first%20mentor%20and%20dear%20friend%2C%20the%20great%20Indian%20poet%20and%20art%20critic%20Nissim%20Ezekiel%2C%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Bene%20Israel%20community.%20Indeed%2C%20one%20of%20my%20great-aunts%2C%20Kitty%20Shiva%20Rao%2C%20was%20born%20Kitty%20Verst%C3%A4ndig%20in%20a%20Viennese%20Jewish%20family%3B%20she%20made%20her%20home%20in%20a%20newly%20independent%20India%2C%20applying%20her%20knowledge%20of%20the%20Holocaust%20to%20healing%20a%20young%20country%20that%20had%20been%20born%20amidst%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20Partition.%20The%20Shoah%20is%20not%20external%20to%20me%3B%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20strands%20in%20my%20own%20family%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Putting%20aside%20biographical%20factors%2C%20I%20wish%20to%20place%20on%20record%20also%20that%20I%20have%20publicly%20opposed%20the%20intellectual%20and%20cultural%20boycott%20of%20Israel%E2%80%94on%20the%20grounds%20that%20this%20will%20further%20weaken%20and%20isolate%20our%20liberal%2C%20progressive%2C%20critical%2C%20and%20inclusive%20colleagues%20within%20Israel.%20I%20do%20not%20share%20the%20BDS%20position%2C%20and%20disagree%20with%20it.%20My%20heart%20goes%20out%20both%20to%20the%20Jewish%20people%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20who%20have%20suffered%20an%20unremitting%20condition%20of%20strife%20for%20more%20than%20seven%20decades%20in%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20condemn%20unequivocally%20the%20terror%20unleashed%20by%20Hamas%20against%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20and%20the%20horrendous%20massacre%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20of%20Israeli%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%20as%20well%20as%20Palestinian%2C%20Thai%2C%20Filipino%2C%20Nepali%2C%20and%20other%20individuals.%20I%20mourn%20the%20deaths%20of%20these%20innocent%20people.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20cannot%20ignore%20the%20brutal%20program%20of%20annihilation%20that%20the%20government%20of%20Israel%20has%20launched%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20civilian%20population%2C%20in%20retaliation.%20I%20cannot%20look%20away%20from%20this%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%2C%20its%20cost%20exacted%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20innocent%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children.%20Now%2C%20more%20than%20ever%2C%20there%20is%20a%20compelling%20need%20to%20bring%20the%20communities%20of%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20together%2C%20to%20renounce%20the%20exceptionalism%20of%20suffering%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20and%20to%20craft%20a%20solidarity%20of%20grief%2C%20a%20communion%20of%20shared%20vulnerability%2C%20and%20a%20process%20of%20healing%20and%20renewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Let%20us%20now%20consider%20the%20so-called%20evidence%20that%20has%20been%20presented%20against%20me%3A%20my%20signature%20on%20a%20petition%20circulated%20by%20the%20Indian%20Cultural%20Forum%20and%20dated%20August%2026%2C%202019%2C%20protesting%20a%20discussion%20hosted%20by%20the%20Consulate%20General%20of%20Israel%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20on%20%E2%80%9CLeaders%E2%80%99%20Idea%20of%20Nations%3A%20Zionism%20and%20Hindutva.%E2%80%9D%20The%20invitation%20for%20this%20event%20presented%20a%20portrait%20of%20Theodor%20Herzl%2C%20the%20founding%20figure%20of%20Zionism%2C%20alongside%20a%20portrait%20of%20V.%20D.%20Savarkar%2C%20a%20founding%20figure%20of%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20reason%20for%20signing%20this%20petition%20was%20because%20the%20event%20clearly%20posited%20an%20equivalence%20between%20Herzl%20and%20Savarkar%2C%20and%20was%20intended%20to%20develop%20intellectual%20respectability%20for%20an%20alliance%20between%20Zionism%20and%20Hindutva.%20I%20found%20this%20highly%20ironic%2C%20since%20Savarkar%20was%20known%20to%20be%20an%20admirer%20of%20Hitler%20and%20openly%20expressed%20his%20admiration%20for%20Nazi%20ideology%20and%20methods%2C%20which%20he%20proposed%20as%20a%20model%20for%20a%20Hindu-majoritarian%20India%20to%20follow%2C%20especially%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20treatment%20of%20the%20religious%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20member%20of%20the%20German%20commentariat%20who%20denounced%20me%20has%20asked%20herself%20or%20himself%20why%20the%20Israeli%20Consulate%20General%20thought%20it%20appropriate%20to%20equate%20Zionism%20with%20Hindutva%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20dedicated%20my%20life%20to%20opposing%20authoritarian%20forces%20and%20discriminatory%20ideologies%2C%20and%20my%20signature%20carried%20with%20it%20the%20weight%20of%20my%20commitment%20to%20dialogue%2C%20inclusiveness%2C%20mutuality%2C%20and%20the%20ceaseless%20quest%20for%20common%20ground.%20This%20commitment%20remains%20with%20me%2C%20as%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20warm%20good%20wishes%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjit%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699967704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F16120251%2FhmvmTUr5_400x400.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcurator-ranjit-hoskote-resigns-from-documentas-finding-committee-over-anti-semitism-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hoskote%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20escalating%20scandals%20that%20have%20followed%20an%20anti-BDS%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20German%20parliament%20in%202019%2C%20with%20artists%20and%20curators%20increasingly%20finding%20themselves%20targeted%20by%20weaponised%20accusations%20of%20anti-Semitism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcurator-ranjit-hoskote-resigns-from-documentas-finding-committee-over-anti-semitism-allegations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Truth%20That%20Modi%20Chose%20to%20Overlook%20About%20Nitish's%20Outbursts%20Against%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14164628%2FThe-Wire-76.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20recently%C2%A0described%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Enirlajja%3C%2Fem%3E%20(shameless)%E2%80%9D%20reacting%20to%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20comment%20that%20it%20was%20his%20%E2%80%9Cfoolishness%E2%80%9D%20that%20led%20him%20to%20get%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20to%20replace%20him%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20was%20addressing%20an%20election%20rally%20to%20seek%20votes%20for%20his%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20at%20Secunderabad%20in%20Telangana%20on%20November%2011%20when%20he%20reacted%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20outburst%20in%20the%20Bihar%20assembly%20on%20November%209.%20%E2%80%9CNitish%20was%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20insulting%20the%20Dalits%20repeatedly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20known%20what%20political%20mileage%20the%20BJP%20would%20derive%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20by%20Modi%20calling%20Nitish%20a%20%E2%80%9Chabitual%20assaulter%E2%80%9D.%20Modi%20also%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20benefactor%20of%20the%20Dalits%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20had%20stood%20with%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20son%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Dalit%20leader%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20%E2%80%9Cwhom%20Nitish%20insulted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20Bihar%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20were%20relatively%20subdued%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%20raising%20the%20quota%20for%20the%20backward%20classes%20and%20the%20Dalits%20to%2065%25%20in%20the%20government%20jobs%2C%20followed%20up%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20comments%20to%20step%20up%20their%20attack%20on%20Nitish.%20The%20development%20has%20surprised%20the%20neutral%20observers%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20the%20ones%2C%20who%20had%20closely%20watched%20the%20situation%20in%20which%20Nitish%20had%20%E2%80%98installed%E2%80%99%20Manjhi%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20owning%20responsibility%20for%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%E2%80%99s%20poor%20performance%20in%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20had%20imagined%20at%20that%20time%20that%20Nitish%20%E2%80%93%20the%20supreme%20leader%20of%20his%20party%20who%20had%20staged%20a%20comeback%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20after%20securing%20unprecedented%20victory%20for%20the%20JDU-BJP%20alliance%20with%20210%20seats%20in%20243%20member-Bihar%20assembly%20in%202010%20assembly%20polls%20%E2%80%93%20would%20demit%20his%20position%20in%20favour%20of%20someone%20else%20after%20the%20BJP%20had%20done%20well%20in%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20performed%20majestically%20in%20all%20the%20north%20Indian%20states%20in%202014%20and%20Bihar%20was%20not%20an%20exception.%20And%20it%20was%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20fought%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Modi%20against%20the%20Congress.%20In%20no%20way%2C%20Nitish%20could%20have%20been%20made%20accountable%20for%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20poor%20show%20in%20that%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06122347%2FF63GTNNWMAAsSYi.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06122347%2FF63GTNNWMAAsSYi.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06122347%2FF63GTNNWMAAsSYi-300x202.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06122347%2FF63GTNNWMAAsSYi-1024x688.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678572%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22806%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20in%20Bihar%2C%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20too%20had%20lost%20massively%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20projected%20Modi%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20and%20Modi%20had%20created%20waves%20in%20his%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2014%20scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20on%20May%2020%2C%202014.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20was%20over%20and%20preparations%20were%20afoot%20for%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20take%20over%20from%20Manmohan%20Singh%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20called%20the%20meeting%20of%20his%20JD(U)%20legislature%20party%20and%20announced%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20own%20the%20moral%20responsibility%20of%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20at%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20quit%20as%20your%20(JDU%E2%80%99s%20legislature%20party%E2%80%99s)%20leader.%20You%20are%20free%20to%20elect%20anyone%20from%20amongst%20you%20as%20your%20leader.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20about%2010%20am.%C2%A0%20All%20the%20JDU%20MLAs%20were%20stunned.%20They%20collectively%20objected%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20decision%20and%20insisted%20on%20him%20not%20to%20do%20it.%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20senior%20from%20the%20JP%20movement%20days%20in%20the%201970s%20and%20then%20state%20JDU%20president%20Bashishtha%20Narayan%20Singh%20was%20miffed%20at%20Nitsh%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%20president%2C%20Sharad%20Yadav%2C%20landed%20in%20Patna%20at%20noon%2C%20driving%20to%20the%201-Aney%20Marg%20%E2%80%93%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20venue%20of%20the%20JDU%20legislature%20party%20meeting%20%E2%80%93%20to%20oversee%20the%20proceedings.%20The%20JDU%20cadres%20who%20had%20thronged%20in%20thousands%20outside%20the%201-Aney%20Marg%20hit%20out%20at%20Sharad%20Yadav%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20persuade%20Nitish%3B%20we%20will%20have%20to%20go%20by%20his%20decision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20the%20president.%20It%E2%80%99s%20sacrilegious%20that%20you%20are%20unable%20to%20persuade%20Nitish%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Your%20conduct%20is%20not%20acceptable%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20cadre%20was%20heard%20blurting%20angrily%20at%20Sharad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%20kept%20up%20with%20their%20pressure%20on%20Nitish%20to%20withdraw%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20almost%20five%20hours.%20However%2C%20they%20failed%20eventually%20and%20consented%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20nominate%20someone%20in%20his%20place.%20It%20was%20at%20about%202%3A30%20pm%20Nitish%20dropped%20the%20name%20of%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20the%20MLA%20from%20Makhdumpur%20belonging%20to%20the%20Mahadalit%20Musahar%20community%2C%20as%20his%20replacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReluctantly%2C%20the%20party%20MLAs%20acquiesced%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20decision%20but%20they%20got%20the%20resolution%20passed%20that%20specifically%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CManjhi%20will%20remain%20CM%20only%20till%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20present%20assembly%20(2010-2015).%20Nitish%20Kumar%20will%20lead%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20the%202015%20assembly%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Foolish%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98stupid%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98orphan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20interpreted%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20remark%20that%20his%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emurkhata%3C%2Fem%3E%20(foolishness)%20led%20him%20to%20make%20Manjhi%20the%20CM%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Cshameless%20and%20humiliation%20to%20Manjhi%E2%80%9D%20which%20the%20Bihar%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20picked%20up%20to%20launch%20a%20frontal%20attack%20on%20Nitish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20several%20JDU%20cadres%20were%20angry%20at%20Nitish%20for%20demitting%20office%20in%20Majhi%E2%80%99s%20favour.%20They%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20to%20accept%20it.%20Outside%20the%201-Aney%20Marg%2C%20many%20JDU%20cadres%20were%20heard%20using%20the%20words%20like%20%E2%80%9Cfoolish%2C%20stupid%20and%20obstinate%E2%80%9D%20when%20they%20learnt%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20make%20Manjhi%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98hero%E2%80%99%20of%20the%C2%A0Mahadalits%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20bloc%20of%20the%20poor%20communities%20which%20he%20had%20given%20preferential%20treatment%20to%20in%20the%20jobs%2C%20panchayat%20raj%20bodies%20and%20a%20plethora%20of%20other%20welfare%20schemes.%20Manjhi%20was%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20a%20Mahadalit%20community.%20But%20no%20Bihar%20leader%20had%20worked%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20Mahadalits%20in%20the%20manner%20Nitish%20had.%20Even%20the%20Mahadalit%20cadres%20of%20the%20JDU%20were%20pained%20at%20Nitish%20getting%20replaced%20with%20Manjhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20himself%20faced%20the%20cadres%E2%80%99%20angry%20outbursts%20when%20he%20escorted%20Manjhi%20to%20governor%20D.%20Y%20Patil%20and%20returned%20to%20stop%20at%20the%20gathering%20of%20the%20exasperated%20cadres%20with%20Manjhi%20by%20his%20side.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%20you%20the%20CM.%20Who%20has%20allowed%20you%20to%20subvert%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20in%20favour%20of%20your%20personal%20choice%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20angry%20cadre%20shouted%20at%20him.%20Another%20screamed%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20made%20the%20people%20%3Cem%3Eanaath%3C%2Fem%3E%20(orphan)%20by%20relinquishing%20the%20responsibility%20given%20by%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14165552%2F1500x500.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14165552%2F1500x500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14165552%2F1500x500-300x100.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14165552%2F1500x500-1024x341.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684733%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20swearing-in%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%20in%20May%202014.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40jitanrmanjhi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20cadres%20were%20heard%20using%20%E2%80%9Cfoolish%20and%20stupid%E2%80%9D%20words%20to%20describe%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20Nitish%20pacified%20them%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20live%20with%20you%20and%20work%20according%20to%20your%20wishes%20and%20will.%20I%20will%20lead%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20again%20in%202015.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nitish%20said%20that%20he%20made%20Manjhi%20the%20chief%20minister%20out%20of%20his%20%E2%80%9Cfoolishness%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20was%20merely%20repeating%20the%20words%20that%20his%20cadres%20had%20used%20against%20him%20on%20May%2020%2C%202014.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20pre-Narendra%20Modi%20era%20media%20was%20sympathetic%20to%20Nitish.%20A%20few%20months%20before%20making%20Manjhi%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Nitish%20vacated%20his%20chair%20for%20Dasrath%20Manjhi%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Mahadalit%20cultivator%20who%20had%20cut%20the%20rocks%20with%20the%20shovel%20and%20spade%20to%20make%20a%20path%20in%20the%20mountains%20of%20Gaya.%20The%20media%20had%20equated%20Manjhi%E2%80%99s%20installation%20with%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20symbolic%20gesture%20for%20Dasrath%20Manjhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManjhi%E2%80%99s%20U-turn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20making%20Manjhi%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Nitish%20formed%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20the%20Congress%20and%20fanned%20out%20in%20the%20north%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Champaran%20region%20to%20organise%20the%20electorate%20against%20the%20BJP.%20Jitan%20Manjhi%20stayed%20silent%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%20following%20up%20on%20the%20development%20work%20and%20welfare%20initiatives%20that%20Nitish%20had%20undertaken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20too%20embarked%20on%20the%20tours%20across%20the%20state%20causing%20embarrassing%20situations%20for%20Nitish%20by%20his%20%E2%80%98bizarre%E2%80%99%20conduct%20and%20utterances.%20At%20a%20public%20meeting%20at%20Darbhanga%2C%20he%20said%20that%20a%20temple%20was%20washed%20after%20he%20offered%20prayer%20in%20it%20and%20was%20found%20wrong%20by%20an%20inquiry%20committee.%20He%20described%20the%20upper%20castes%20as%20%E2%80%9Cforeigners%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20Dalits%20as%20%E2%80%9Caborigines%E2%80%9D%20and%20derided%20the%20lower%20caste%20women%20who%20had%20their%20husbands%20working%20in%20other%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-jitan-ram-manjhi-exit-mahagathbandhan%5C%22%3EBihar%3A%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%E2%80%99s%20Potential%20Exit%20Will%20Not%20Worry%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20JDU%20cadres%20were%20up%20in%20arms%20against%20Manjhi%20parading%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20demanding%20Nitish%20to%20replace%20him.%20But%20when%20the%202015%20assembly%20elections%20drew%20close%20and%20the%20party%20leadership%20demanded%20Majhi%20to%20demit%20the%20office%20in%20favour%20of%C2%A0%20Nitish%2C%20Manjhi%20rebelled%20levelling%20%E2%80%98insult%E2%80%99%20to%20him%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Celitist%E2%80%9D%20JDU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20after%20a%20long%20and%20strenuous%20effort%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Sharad%20Yadav%2C%20Bashishtha%20Narayan%20Singh%2C%20and%20others%20in%20the%20party%2C%20Manjhi%20stepped%20down%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%20But%2C%20after%20he%20stepped%20down%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20Jitan%20Manjhi%20made%20his%20own%20party%20%E2%80%93%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20(Secular)%20%E2%80%93%20that%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202015%20assembly%20elections%20against%20the%20Nitish-led%20JDU-RJD-Congress%20Mahagathbandhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1700462521000000%26usg%3DAOvVaw2-eWIxEMgG1CAj-Gsha6XF%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%253Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%2526source%253Dgmail-imap%2526ust%253D1700462521000000%2526usg%253DAOvVaw2-eWIxEMgG1CAj-Gsha6XF%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1700030303126000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVa