%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333785%2Fdiwali-decor-ideas-for-home-ecofriendly-lamps-rangoli-fairy-lights%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20You%20Know%3F%20National%20Flags%20at%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20Are%20Made%20of%20Recycled%20PET%20Bottles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20sponsored%20by%20Coca-Cola%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20kicked%20off%20on%205%20October%2C%202023%2C%20with%20an%20inspiring%20and%20sustainable%20twist%20as%20Coca-Cola%20India%20%E2%80%94%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20%E2%80%94%20introduced%20a%20pioneering%20initiative%20in%20the%20world%20of%20cricket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECelebrating%20the%20shared%20passion%20for%20the%20sport%20and%20a%20dedication%20to%20sustainability%2C%20Coca-Cola%20India%20and%20ICC%20unveiled%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20post-consumer%20PET%20bottles%2C%20making%20this%20global%20sporting%20event%20a%20platform%20for%20promoting%20environmental%20responsibility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPET%20bottles%20were%20ingeniously%20transformed%20into%20yarn%2C%20which%20was%20then%20skillfully%20crafted%20into%20flags.%20These%20flags%20played%20a%20prominent%20role%20in%20the%20pre-match%20national%20anthem%20ceremony%20at%20stadiums%20throughout%20the%20tournament.%20Coca-Cola%20India%20oversaw%20the%20creation%20of%20national%20flags%20for%20all%2010%20participating%20nations%2C%20as%20well%20as%2010%20ICC%20unity%20flags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20environmental%20initiative%20ushered%20in%20a%20new%20era%20of%20responsibility%20and%20sustainability%2C%20showcasing%20Coca-Cola%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20a%20greener%20future.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20Coca-Cola%20and%20ICC%20became%20the%20first%20companies%20worldwide%20to%20introduce%20recycled%20PET%20national%20flags%20to%20the%20game%20of%20cricket%2C%20setting%20a%20precedent%20for%20future%20sporting%20events.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CInnovation%20and%20sustainability%20take%20center%20stage%20at%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20where%20national%20flags%2C%20embodying%20unity%2C%20and%20pride%2C%20are%20now%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20PET%20bottles.%20With%20Coca-Cola%20India%E2%80%99s%20collaboration%2C%20we%20have%20introduced%20a%20groundbreaking%20environmental%20initiative%2C%20symbolizing%20our%20collective%20pledge%20towards%20a%20more%20eco-friendly%20future%20and%20a%20sustainable%20sports%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20stated%20an%20%3Cstrong%3EICC%20Head%20of%20Events%2C%20Chris%20Tetley.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20showcased%20environmental%20responsibility%20by%20unveiling%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20PET%20bottles.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334072%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20showcased%20environmental%20responsibility%20by%20unveiling%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20PET%20bottles.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20these%20exceptional%20flags%20to%20life%2C%20approximately%2011%2C000%20PET%20bottles%20were%20used%20to%20create%20each%20national%20flag%2C%20while%20approximately%202%2C000%20PET%20bottles%20were%20utilised%20for%20each%20ICC%20unity%20flag.%20The%20flags%20were%20skillfully%20manufactured%20by%20GoRevise%20%E2%80%94%20a%20division%20of%20Ganesha%20Ecoverse%20Limited%20%E2%80%94%20which%20specialises%20in%20the%20production%20of%20recycled%20yarn%20and%20garments.%20Over%20100%20dedicated%20workers%20contributed%20their%20time%20and%20effort%2C%20working%20tirelessly%20for%2025%20days%20and%20clocking%20over%20300%20hours%20to%20produce%20these%20flags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20thrilled%20to%20announce%20Coca-Cola%20India%20%E2%80%94%20partnering%20with%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Go%20Rewise.%20Together%2C%20we%20have%20made%20history%20at%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20by%20unveiling%20the%20National%20Flags%20of%20each%20country%20participating%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20ICC%20Unity%20Flag.%20These%20flags%20are%20a%20first%20in%20cricket%20worldwide%2C%20made%20entirely%20from%20Recycled%20PET%20bottles.%20India%20is%20celebrating%2C%20and%20we%20at%20Go%20Rewise%20are%20equally%20delighted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20incredible%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20%3Cstrong%3ESandeep%20Khandelwal%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Ganesha%20Ecosphere%20and%20Managing%20Director%2C%20Ganesha%20Ecoverse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola%20India%20initiated%20both-%20online%20and%20offline%20(on-ground)%20initiatives%20throughout%20the%20tournament%2C%20aimed%20at%20engaging%20fans%20and%20consumers%20and%20raising%20awareness%20about%20waste%20management.%20The%20Company%20is%20facilitating%20waste%20management%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%23MaidaanSaaf%20campaign%20and%20has%20installed%20reverse%20vending%20machines%20at%20all%20the%20stadiums%20for%20the%20collection%20of%20consumed%20PET.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArnab%20Roy%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Marketing%2C%20Coca-Cola%20India%20%26amp%3B%20Southwest%20Asia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20expressed%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CCoca-Cola%20has%20a%20mission%20to%20support%20sustainability%20efforts%20as%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20all%20sporting%20events.%20Aligned%20with%20this%20mission%2C%20we%20take%20pride%20in%20unveiling%20national%20flags%20made%20with%20recycled%20PET%20at%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20today.%20With%20these%20recycled%20national%20and%20ICC%20unity%20flags%20we%20are%20dedicated%20to%20advancing%20the%20principles%20of%20a%20circular%20economy.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20significance%20of%20sports%20and%20cricket%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20millions%20in%20India%2C%20Coca-Cola%20India%2C%20and%20ICC%20intend%20to%20showcase%20their%20commitment%20to%20creating%20a%20sustainable%20sporting%20experience%20during%20this%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699677000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Celebrating%20the%20shared%20passion%20for%20cricket%20and%20a%20dedication%20to%20sustainability%2C%20Coca-Cola%20India%20and%20ICC%20unveiled%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20post-consumer%20PET%20bottles%2C%20making%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20tournament%20a%20platform%20for%20promoting%20environmental%20responsibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pranita%20Bhat%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334067%2Ficc-mens-cricket-world-cup-coca-cola-unveils-national-flags-made-from-recycled-pet-bottles%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IAS%20Coaching%20Centre%20Fined%20Rs%205%20Lakh%20for%20Misleading%20Ads%20With%20Toppers%3A%20Red%20Flags%20You%20Should%20Check%20For%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Consumer%20Protection%20Authority%20(CCPA)%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20on%20Khan%20Study%20Group%20(KSG)%2C%20a%20coaching%20institute%20in%20India%2C%20on%20account%20of%20unfair%20trade%20practices%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F158493%2Fadvertising-misleading-ads-legal-recourse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emisleading%20advertising%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20action%20comes%20after%20observing%20various%20civil%20services%20exam%20coaching%20centres%20which%20post%20advertisements%20claiming%20successful%20candidates%20to%20be%20their%20students.%20These%20institutes%20use%20pictures%20and%20names%20of%20toppers%20without%20indicating%20the%20length%20of%20the%20course%2C%20the%20fees%20paid%20or%20the%20course%20opted%20to%20lure%20prospective%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20advertisement%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20valid%20and%20not%20deceitful%20when%20it%20does%20not%20mislead%20consumers%20by%20exaggerating%20the%20usefulness%20of%20the%20products%20or%20services%2C%20says%20the%20consumer%20affairs%20ministry.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKSG%20was%20found%20making%20false%20claims%20such%20as%20682%20out%20of%20933%20selected%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333846%2Fhyderabad-balalatha-mallavarapu-affected-by-polio-crack-upsc-cse-without-coaching-teaches-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20students%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20from%20KSG.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20DG%20(Investigation)%20CCPA%20was%20asked%20for%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20into%20the%20matters%20and%20it%20was%20found%20in%20the%20investigation%20report%20that%20out%20of%20682%2C%20only%20eight%20successful%20candidates%20took%20guidance%20for%20additional%20courses%20and%20that%20too%20in%20previous%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20those%208%2C%20the%20five%20toppers%20only%20took%20mock%20interview%20programmes%20from%20Khan%20Study%20Group%20which%20were%20free%20of%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20being%20lured%20by%20such%20scams%2C%20here%20are%20a%20few%20red%20flags%20to%20spot%20as%20suggested%20by%20Aakarsh%20Agarwal%2C%20a%20motivational%20speaker%2C%20lawyer%2C%20and%20financial%20guide%20on%20Quora.%20Aakarsh%20has%20over%204%20lakh%20views%20on%20his%20profile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Do%20not%20fall%20for%20unrealistic%20success%20rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coaching%20centre%20claiming%20a%2099%20percent%20or%20100%20percent%20success%20rate%20is%20a%20big%20red%20flag%20according%20to%20Aakarsh.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20success%20rates%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20a%20number%20of%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20the%20difficulty%20level%20of%20the%20exam%20and%20the%20individual%20abilities%20of%20the%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Beware%20of%20fake%20reviews%20and%20testimonials%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkarsh%20says%20that%20if%20there%20are%20too%20many%20good%20reviews%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F262120%2Fjharkhand-free-online-classes-zoom-youtube-paathshala-upsc-examinations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20coaching%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%20they%20might%20be%20fake.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20try%20to%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20reviews%20by%20checking%20if%20they%20are%20from%20real%20people%20and%20if%20they%20have%20similar%20language%20or%20writing%20styles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Ask%20for%20result%20verification%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20suggests%20asking%20for%20verification%20of%20all%20the%20good%20results%20the%20institute%20is%20claiming.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20provide%20proof%20of%20their%20students%E2%80%99%20success%2C%20such%20as%20exam%20scores%20or%20certificates%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20red%20flag.%20A%20reputable%20coaching%20centre%20should%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20upon%20request%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Check%20for%20accreditation%20or%20certification%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20red%20flag%20that%20he%20suggests%20that%20everyone%20should%20watch%20out%20for%20is%20certification.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20accredited%20or%20certified%20by%20a%20recognised%20organisation%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20sign%20that%20they%20are%20not%20meeting%20certain%20standards%20or%20regulations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Lack%20of%20transparency%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20transparent%20about%20its%20teaching%20methods%2C%20course%20materials%2C%20or%20success%20rates%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%20A%20reputable%20coaching%20centre%20should%20be%20willing%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20to%20prospective%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aakarsh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699627832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Searching%20for%20the%20best%20UPSC%20coaching%20institute%3F%20The%20Central%20Consumer%20Protection%20Authority%20(CCPA)%20has%20just%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%205%20Lakh%20on%20Khan%20Study%20Group%20(KSG)%20for%20misleading%20ads%20with%20IAS%20toppers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334054%2Fccpa-fines-khan-study-group-how-to-choose-upsc-coaching-centre-in-delhi-ias-toppers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20Was%2017%20When%20I%20Joined%20Netaji%E2%80%99s%20Fight%20for%20Freedom%3A%2095-YO%20%E2%80%98Asha%20San%E2%80%99%20Shares%20Her%20Incredible%20Story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%201943%2C%20when%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20managed%20to%20reach%20Japan%20in%20a%20submarine%20via%20Germany%20to%20lead%20the%20freedom%20movement%20in%20East%20Asia%2C%20a%20young%2C%20skinny%20teenager%20went%20to%20him%20to%20express%20her%20decision%20of%20helping%20him%20fight%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%2015-year-old%2C%20Netaji%20convinced%20the%20girl%20that%20she%20was%20too%20young%20to%20join%20the%20regiment.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20the%20headstrong%20teenager%20was%20again%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20him%20demanding%20to%20let%20her%20join%20the%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20Japan%20amid%20the%20bombings%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20she%20never%20feared%20a%20war.%20Impressed%20by%20her%20resolve%2C%20Netaji%20welcomed%20her%20to%20join%20the%20newly-formed%20women%20regiment%20that%20was%20made%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20overthrowing%20the%20British%20Raj%20in%20colonial%20India%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20the%20Japanes