n%20no%20one%20in%20power%20listened%20to%20them%2C%20they%20approached%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20and%20filed%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20decision%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20three%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Natasha%2C%20Pranay%20Juvvadi%2C%20and%20Tejah%20%E2%80%94%20became%20applicants%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20remaining%20citizens%20kept%20organising%20awareness%20campaigns%20across%20the%20city%20to%20make%20authorities%20understand%20why%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20save%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F138262%2Fpillalamarri-mahabubnagar-telengana-banyan-tree%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiant%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20recent%20decision%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20is%20a%20big%20win%20for%20citizens.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333927%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20recent%20decision%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20is%20a%20big%20win%20for%20the%20citizens.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20on%207%20November%202023%2C%20the%20NGT%20directed%20the%20NHAI%20to%20conduct%20an%20EIA.%20The%20NGT%20has%20also%20directed%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20and%20Forests%20to%20issue%20the%20Terms%20of%20Reference%20(ToR)%20at%20the%20earliest%20and%20complete%20the%20process%20within%20four%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20welcome%20the%20decision%2C%20but%20the%20battle%20is%20not%20won%20yet.%20It%20is%20a%20small%20victory%20but%20we%20are%20not%20being%20complacent%20about%20it.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20the%20kind%20of%20report%20NHAI%20will%20come%20up%20with%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Asiya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20fight%20authorities%20as%20individuals%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejah%20adds%20that%20the%20judgment%20is%20unique%20and%20will%20be%20exemplary%20for%20people%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20any%20such%20examples%20where%20people%20rose%20against%20the%20authorities%20to%20protect%20natural%20landforms.%20Others%20can%20use%20this%20judgement%20as%20a%20precedent%20which%20was%20not%20an%20option%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20their%20experiences%2C%20Tejah%20also%20shares%20five%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20fight%20for%20public%20and%20natural%20properties%20as%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Come%20together%20as%20a%20group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Tejah%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20a%20big%20non-profit%20organisation%20or%20any%20powerful%20agency%2C%20we%20are%20just%20a%20group%20of%20citizens.%20The%20reason%20why%20we%20won%20is%20that%20we%20picked%20a%20specific%20issue%2C%20came%20together%2C%20and%20fought%20the%20case%20to%20the%20very%20end.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEngage%20people%20from%20across%20diverse%20cultures%2C%20backgrounds%2C%20and%20age%20groups.%20Build%20a%20group%20that%20is%20as%20broad%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20banyans%20form%20an%20ecological%20corridor%20connecting%20different%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20state%20for%20many%20birds%20and%20other%20species.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333929%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20banyans%20form%20an%20ecological%20corridor%20connecting%20different%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20state%20for%20many%20birds%20and%20other%20species.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Do%20not%20doubt%20yourself%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20us%20are%20lawyers%2C%20professionals%2C%20or%20in%20power.%20But%20we%20put%20in%20our%20time%20to%20read%20and%20speak%20to%20experts%20to%20understand%20the%20cause.%20It%20was%20not%20impossible.%20If%20we%20could%20do%20it%2C%20others%20can%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20four%20years%20back%2C%20somebody%20asked%20me%20to%20head%20a%20petition%20like%20this%2C%20I%20would%20have%20ended%20up%20laughing%20and%20questioning%20my%20abilities.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20could%20not%20differentiate%20between%20the%20varieties%20of%20trees.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20learning%20process%20for%20me%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20It%20is%20not%20good%20vs%20evil%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NHAI%20is%20doing%20its%20job.%20So%2C%20ideally%2C%20there%20are%20no%20real%20villains.%20However%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20highlight%20what%20constitutes%20a%20public%20benefit%20and%20a%20better%20society%2C%20and%20how%20development%20projects%20should%20learn%20to%20incorporate%20nature%20and%20rethink%20these%20definitions%20in%20the%20context%20of%20climate%20change%20and%20better%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Understand%20what%20is%20legally%20possible%20and%20legally%20viable%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETejah%20points%20out%20that%20as%20citizens%2C%20we%20may%20think%20that%20the%20national%20tree%20of%20India%20will%20have%20some%20legal%20protection%20but%20apparently%20they%20don%E2%80%99t.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20have%20to%20negotiate%20a%20space%20for%20them%20in%20our%20legal%20framework.%20What%20we%20think%20is%20legal%20and%20what%20is%20viable%20become%20two%20different%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5)%20Do%20not%20get%20overwhelmed%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20nature%20is%20to%20produce%20volumes%20of%20documentation.%20Our%20job%20is%20to%20try%20to%20understand%20what%20these%20documents%20are%20and%20seek%20experts%E2%80%99%20help%20whenever%20required.%20Have%20patience%20in%20understanding%20documents%20and%20Excel%20sheets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ENature%20Lovers%20of%20Hyderabad%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699539603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333910%