%20is%20staying%20away%20from%20her%20child%3F%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20my%20fate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20sadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20death%20of%20their%20parents%2C%20Sangeeta%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20manage%20her%20brother%20Rajiv%20Rao%2C%2034%2C%20who%20has%20a%20mental%20disability%2C%20when%20she%20went%20to%20work.%C2%A0%20He%20was%20brought%20to%20Sangopita%20in%202009%20and%20his%20progress%20has%20been%20very%20good%20since%20then%2C%20shares%20Sangeeta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20very%20clever.%20When%20my%20father%20was%20alive%2C%20we%20had%20to%20keep%20a%20watch%20on%20Rajiv%20all%20the%20time%20as%20he%20would%20often%20drink%20alcohol%20or%20find%20some%20tobacco.%20With%20Sangopita%2C%20he%20has%20multiple%20avenues%20to%20spend%20his%20energy%20the%20right%20way.%20He%20makes%20%3Cem%3Eagarbattis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(incense%20sticks)%2C%20paints%20and%20%3Cem%3Ediyas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(earthen%20lamps)%20there%20and%20is%20doing%20very%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20progress%20in%20children%20that%20the%20Sugwekars%20strive%20so%20hard%20for.%20Ravindra%20quit%20his%20job%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20and%20the%20couple%20is%20engaged%20full-time%20in%20this%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20them%20to%20have%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329201%2Fgrailmaker-innovations-vision-nanny-platform-app-solution-for-kids-cortical-visual-impairment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenjoyable%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20fulfil%20their%20needs.%20We%20keep%20them%20active%20with%20sports%2C%20music%2C%20arts%20and%20craft.%20Many%20of%20the%20admittees%20have%20stopped%20their%20sleeping%20pills%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ravindra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20encourage%20the%20people%20in%20their%20shelters%20to%20make%20products%20like%20%3Cem%3Ediyas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cards%20on%20occasions%20like%20Diwali%20and%2